Malawi ichateedza imba neimba ichiongorora ropa maringe nedenda reshuramatongo
Vanhu vemuMalawi vane maonera akasiyana pamusoro pehurongwa hwehurumende hwekutanga kuongorora ropa kuitira reshuramatongo gore rinouya richingotanga, ichiita zvekuteedza imba neimba.
Vanotsigira zano iri vanoti chirongwa ichi chinyanya kudiwa nekuti vanhu vemuMulawi zana vanobata chirwere ichi zuva nezuva, uye vanhu vangasvike zana nemakumi matatu nemasere vanofa nekuda kweshuramatongo zuva nezuva.
Gurokota rezvehutano Jean Kalirani avakazivisa hurongwa uhwu pamusi wekucherechedza zuva reshuramatongo reWorld AIDS Day rakaitwa muchinguva chichangodarika mudunhu rekumaodzanyemba reKaronga.
Tichaenda kumamisha tichikumbira kutora madonhwe eropa kuti tione kuti munhu anedenda reshuramatongo here kana kuti kwete.
Vose vanenge vawanikwa vaine denda reshuramatongo zvirokwazvo vachapihwa kubatsirwa nekuchengetwa kwavanenge vachida.
Uye avo venenge vawanikwa vasina denda iri vachapihwa mazano kuitira kuti varambe vasina denda iri, akadaro Kalirani.
Kalirani akati chirongwa ichi chichatanga pakati paKurume uye chichange chiine donzvo rekubata munhu wese munyika, kusanganisira vanhu vari kure nenzvimbo dzinobatsira nezvehutano nekuongorora ropa pane zveshuramatongo nekupa mazano nezvedenda iri.
Vakati hurongwa uhwu hwuri maringe nechinangwa chekupedza shuramatongo panosvika gore ra2030.
Hwuwandu hwekupararira kwedenda reshuramatongo muMalawi ikezvino huri pazvikamu gumi kubva pazana, zvichiratidza kuderera zvishoma kubva pane zvakange zviri makore matatu apfuura.
Chiziviso ichi chakaunza kuvhunduka nekutya mukati mevamwe vanhu vemuMalawi, saSteven Jailosi, mudzidzisi wechikoro chevana vadiki mumaruwa eBlantyre, anofunga kuti chirongwa ichi chichabvongodza nekufumura zvhinhu zvevanhu zvavanoda kuti zvive zvakavanzikana.
Handifunge kuti zvakanaka nekuti vanenge vopindira vasina kutenderwa kuti vazive zvakavanzikana zvedu.
Kuongororwa ropa maringe nedenda resurmatongo chinofanirwa kuva chinhu chinoitwa pakavanzikana. Hapana anofanirwa kuziva kuti ndakaenda kunoongorwa ropa, kuzhe kwekuti ndaita sarudzo yekuvaudza, akadaro Jailosi.
Ester Makonokaya, anoshanda semunyori muBlantyre, akati kunyangwe akatoongorwa ropa rake kare, anofunga kuti zvekuteedza imba neimba kuchiongorora ropa maringe neshuramatongo zvinofumura zvakavanzikana zvevanhu.
Hurumende inofanirwa kuendesa zvipatara zvinotenderera zvichienda kumamisha uko vanhu vanogona kuzviendera vega vasarudza kudaro, pane zvekunovangorora ropa ravo mudzimba dzavo, nekuti izvi zvinogona kuita kuti vanhu vanga vasiingafanirwe kuziva chimiro chehutano hwemunhu vanopedzesera voziva, sezvamunozuiva, kana munhu angororwa ropa pane zvaunoita maringe nezvabuda mukuongorwa uku, akadaro Makonokaya.
Macpherson Maulana, mutori wenhau muBlantyre uye ari mugadziri hwezvirongwa zvehutano pawairesi, akaudza VOA kuti zviri nani kuti hurumende idzidzise vanhu vemuMalawi zvakakoshera kuongororwa ropa kuti munhu azive kuti ane denda remashuratongo here kana kuti kwete, kuitira kuti vanhu vagozviita vega "vasina kusundwa nekumanikidzwa."
I fear it could end up into fights. You see it happened in Liberia recently where people who were coming to help people suspected to have contracted Ebola were even killed. So, civic education is the most important element for people to be encouraged to come out for testing voluntarily, said Maulana.
Saka, dzidziso kuvagari ndicho chinhu chakanyanyokosha kuti vanhu vakurudzirwe kuti vabude vachizviuyira vega kuzoongororwa vasina kumanikidzwa, akadaro Maulana.
Zvisineyi, mubatsiri anotaura nevanhu nekuvapa mazano pamusoro pechirwere cheshuramatongo anonzi David Odali, uyo ane sangano rake rinonzi NGO Umunthu Foundation rine zvirongwa zvine chekuita nedenda reshuramatongo, anosimbisa chose kuti pachave nekuchengetedza zvinofanirwa kuvanzwa zvemunhu.
Kuchengetedzeka kwezvakavanzikana zvevanhu kuchavepo. Ngatifungeyiwo pamusoro pemariro kaita misha yakasiyanana siyana. Ndinofunga kuti chimhu chekutanga kupa dzidziso nemazano kuvanhu vemhuri iyi. Hongu, vanhu vanogona kuongororwa vamwe vakatarisa, asi kana tasvika pakuzivisa zvabuda muongoro, anodzidzisa nekupa mazano ezvehutano anofanirwa kuudza mabuda muongoro kumunhu nemunhu akazvimiririra, akadaro Odali.
