Odali akati zvinenge zviri kumunhu anenge aongororwa kuti azivise kuti ropa rake rakamira papi.
Odali said it will be up to the person who has been tested to disclose his or her status.
In 2006, the charity Development Aid from People to People conducted door-to-door HIV testing in the district of Thyolo and Blantyre, reaching 400,000 people. The organization says it worked well.
Kushaikwa Kwemvura Kokonzera Kutyira Zvirwere Zvinaowanikwa Mumvura MuMalawi
Vanhu veBlantyre, guta guru pane zvehupfumi muMalawi, vanowanzoshandisa mvura inobuda mupombi.
Asi kwemwedzi mishanu yadarika mapombi aya angaoma kuti papata, izvo zviri kumanikidza vagari kuti vachere mvura kubva munzvimbo dzisina kuchengetedzeka zvakaita senzizi yematsime, vakamirira kuti basa rekugadzirisa mishina inopomba mvura muguta iri.
Njodzi yekubata zvirwere zvinogara mumvura iri kuramba ichisimuka.
MuBlantyre nenzvimbo dzakaipoteredza, vagari vakagara mazuva mashanu vasina mvura inobuda mupombi.
Madzimayi, avo maringe netsika yemuMalawi vanoita mabasa epamba, vanogun'una pamusoro penjodzi dzavanosangana nadzo pavanochera mvura kubva munzizi dziri munzvimbo dzinogara vanhu.
Rhoda Milanzi, mudzimayi anogara pamba vari mai vevana vatatu, vsnoudza VOA kuti zhiras dzekupfuura nemuzvikwenzi dzine njodzi.
"Tinomuka pakati pehusiku, nguva dzeku 2 a.m., dzimwe nguva kuma 1 a.m., kuti tiende kunochera mvura.
Kune njodzi dzakawanda.
Unoona, dzimwe nguva taisanga nevaroyi, nenyoka muzhira," anodaro, "kunyangwe mapere anotitandanisa."
Milanzi anoti kuti zvisanyanye kuvaremera kusenga mvura yakawanda yekugeza, madzimayi avakusarudza kugeza murwizi.
Asi anoti vanokanganiswa nevechidiki vanenge vakahwanda muzvikwenzi zviri pedyo.
Vechidiki vanhasi ava vaiuya ipapo vagohwandira kuti vatione takashama.
Changa chiri chinyadzo chikuru.
Takatozonogunun'una kumadzimambo pamusoro penyaya iyi.
Vakaranga vamwe vavo, asi unozviva, dzimwe nguva vaikwira mumiti kuti vangoona madzimayi makuru akaita sesu tichigeza, anotsanangura achidaro.
Dambudziko remvura iri rakabva rakanganisa kuwanikwa kwezvehurano.
Masvondo matatu apfuura, vakuru vepachipatara cheQueen Elizabeth Central Hospital muBlantyre vakabvuma kuti vakange vamisa kurapa kunosanganisira kucheka nekuvhura mitezo yemiviri yevanhu nekuda kwekushaikwa kwemvura.
Vanorwira kodzero dzezvehutano vanoyambira kuti panogona kutushuka zvirwere zvinogara mumvura, zvikuru munzvimbo dzinogara vanhu vakawnda, kana nyaya iyi ikasagadziriswa.
Vashandi vakuru pabazi rinoona nezvemvura yemuguta iri, yeBlantyre Water Board vanoti dambudziko iri riri kubva pabasa riri kubhadharirwa mari neEuropean Union rekiisa mishina yekupomba mvura paWalkers Ferry, panova ndipo pane mishina mikuru yekumba mvura.
Priscilla Mateyu, mutauriri weBlantyre Water Board, anoti basa iri riri kutarisirwa kuwedzera mvura inopombwa kuti isvike kuzviuru zana nezvishanu zvema cubic meters pazuva kubva pa cubic metre zviuru makumi manomwe nemaserenari kupombwa pazuva iyezvino.
Ndira ndipo pari kupera basa iri.
Asi kuitira mishina mitsva nezvimwe zvese kuti zvinyatsoshanda zvakanaka, tinotofanira kumiririra kusvikira Kukadzi wa2015.
Ndipo patiri kutarisira kuti huwandu hwemvura hunenge hwakwirira uyewo nekuwedzera kwegoneso yekuburitsa mvura yakawanda inenge ichiitawo zviri nani kusvikira yasvika patinoitarisira kuti ive, Mateyu akadaro.
Sangano rinorwira kodzero dzevatengi muMalawi reConsumers Association of Malawi, rakange ricironga kuita mapungwe pamahofisi ebazi rinoona nezvemvura kusvikira nyaya yemvura yagadziriswa uye mvura yavakubuda mumapombi, asi bazi iri rakati vaida kuratidzira vambomira izvozvo, ndokubva vavimbisa kuunza mvura kuvagari vachishandisa matangi anotendera nemvura.
Sangano iri rakapa bazi rezvemvura kuti rizadzikise chivimbiso charo pasati pava nekuratidzira.
Mutungamiriri weMalawi Opinda Mumoto Nekupa Vatapi Venhau Mari
Mutungamiriri weMalawi vaPeter Mutharika vakapinda mumoto neuti vakapa mahamvuropu ane zana nemakumi maviri ne mashanu emadhora kuvatapi venhau vanodarika makumi masere pamabiko avakaita mwedzi wadarika muBlantyre.
Mupepeti wesangano renhau risiri rehurumende rinonzi Times Television akati vatapi venhau vakaudzwa kuti hamvuropu idzi dzaive nehurongwa hwemutungamiriri wenyika pamusoro pamasangano enhau, ayo anga achitsoropodza zvirikuitwa nehurumende mune zvehupfumi hwenyika.
Muchinyorwa chake chakaburitswa mubepanhau remuMalawi rinonzi Sunday, mupepeti Grecian Tukula akati akange asina chokwadi chekuti seyi mari iyi yakapihwa vapepeti venhau pamabiko ehurumende aya.
Tukula akati akange asarudza kudzorera mari iyi asi ndokuzoshandura pfungwa iyi kuti "asakonzere bopoto."
Asi mupepeti webepanhau rinonzi Weekend Nation, George Kasakula, akaudza VOA kuti akabva adzorera mari iyi ipapo.
Ndakangonzwa mandiri kuti zvakange zvisina kunaka kuti nditambire mari iyi, saka ndakabva ndaidzorera.
Kunzwisisa kwandiinako ndekwekuti kana munhu akandikoka kumusangano uri maringe nebasa ravanoita, ibasa ravo kuona kuti vandipa zvekudya, vondipa pekugara nezvekufambisa.
Asi pachiitiko ichi, handina kuona kuti sei ndaifanirwa kupihwa mari iyi nekuti handina chandakashandisa kuti ndiende kumuzinda wemutungamiriri,wenyia, unonzi Sanjika Palace, akadaro Kasakula.
Nyaya iyi yakwezvawo vanhu veruzhinji mushure mekunge wayiresi isiri mumaoko ehurumende inonzi Capital Radio yakatepfenyura nyaya yaibvunza chirevo chekupa musvo wemari kwakaitwa uku ichibva kumutungamiriri wenyika.
Isu seCapital FM tiripo kuita zvido zveveruzhinji. Nyaya iyi yange yakatekeshera pamadandemutande enhaurirano pamapotonjrtr nenharembozha, uye kunyangwe isu sevenhau, maonerowo edu, kuti takapinzwawo munyaya iyi, saka zvakakosha zvikurusa kuti titeedza munyatso wenyaya iyi kusvikira tasvika pamudzi wayo chaiwo, akadro Steven Dakalira,anotungamirira chikamu chezvenhau nezvirikuitika paCapital Radio.
Nyaya iyi yange yakatekeshera pamadandemutande enhaurirano painternet nenharembozha, uye kunyangwe isu sevenhau, maonerowo edu, kuti takapinzwawo munyaya iyi, saka zvakakosha zvikurusa kuti titeedza munyatso wenyaya iyi kusvikira tasvika pamudzi wayo chaiwo, akadro Steven Dakalira,anotungamirira chikamu chezvenhau nezvirikuitika paCapital Radio.
Muchinyorwa chvo chakabuda mubepanhau reNyasa Times, muzvinafundo mune zvemutemo wemuMalawi Danwood Mzikenge Chirwa vakati zvakaitwa nemutungamiriri wenyika vaMutharika zvekutambidza mari kuvatapi venhau pachiitiko chenhau zvaange zvakafanana nefufuro.
Vakati vaMutharika vanofanirwa kunyora tsamba yekusiya basa kana kuti vomanikidzwa zviri pamutemo kuti vasiye basa nekuti vakatyora mutemo wenyika.
Masangano anorwira kodzero dzevanhu dzakati "nekuti vakaedza kupa fufuro kuvatapi venhau" vaMutharika vakabva vaderedza kuhutungamiriri hwavo kuti humhurwe.
Zvichakadayi, vamwe vatapi venhau varikupa mari iyi kuti ibatsire vanotambura nekushaiwa.
Brian Ligomeka, mupepeti anotungamirira kana kuti Managing Editor wesangano renhau rinonzi the Times Group, akaudza Times Television kuti vatapi venhau vana vesangano rake vaiveko vakapa mari iyi kumusha unochengeta nherera.
Pakutanga takasarudza kudzosera mari iyi kumutungamiriri wenyika, asi takazosarudza kutenga zvinhu zvakasiyana siyana zvakaita setsvigiri, munyu, mabhuku ekunyorera nekuzozvipa kuvana vanotambura, akadaro Ligomeka.
Muchinyorwa chake chinobuda mubepanhau reSunday Times, Raphael Tenthani, uyo anonyorerawo BBC, akakumbira ruregerero akamiririea vamwe vatapi venhau "nekurasisa veruzhinji vanovimba nevatapi venhau pasina kukahadzika."
Tenthani akazopa mari iyi kuti ibatsire vanoshaya, uye akati kunyangwe hazvo vatapi venhau vaizenge vakaita zviri nani deno kuri kunzi vakabva vadzorera mari iyi ipapo, kuita zvakadaro zvinga dai zvakaonekwa sekusaremekedza mukuru wenyika.
Maclan Kanyangwa, uyo anotungamirira bazi rezvekudzidza zvekutapa nhau reDepartment of Journalism and Media Studies paPolytechnic College of the University yemumaMalawi, akati zvisungo zvemabatirwo ebasa rekutapa nhau nodzivisa vatapi venhau kuti vagamuchire mari nekuti vane nyaya vanyora.
Zviri pachena kuti musangano uyu pamuzinda wemutungamiriri chaive chinhu chinokosha panyaya dzekutapa nhau.
Paive nemukana wekuti chimwe chinhu chaizoziviswa.
Uye pamutambo uyu kuzobhadhara vatapi venhau kuti varunzirwe pamanyorero avo nhau izvi zvaizounza dambudziko, akadaro Kanyangwa.
Kanyangwa akati anofunga kuti vatapi venhau vazhinji vakakonewa kudzosera mari iyi ipapo nekuti vakange varivara panyaya yezvisungo zvehunhu hwevatapi venhau panguva yavakatambira mari iyi.
Zvose zvakaitwa kutaura nemubati webasa rezvenhau muhofisi yemutungamiriri wenyika kana kuti Presidential Press Officer, vaFredrick Ndala, hazvina kubudirira.
Asi vamwe vakuru vehurumende vanoti kubhadharwa uku kwaisava kufufura asi yaiva mari yekutsiva mari yakange yashandiswa kuenga mafuta edimotokari dzeavo vakauya kumi=utambo wakaitwa manheru uyu.
Nhau: Kugadzira Zvinhu Kunogona Kudzikinura Nyika Dzakaromboka Kudarika Dzimwe Kubva Kuhurombo
A new United Nations report urges the poorest countries in the world to shift from low- to high-productivity activities to improve their economies.
Muchinyorwa chayo cheongoro netsvarukudzo chegore pamusoro penyika dziri pazasi zasi pane zvebudiriro kana kuti Least Developed Countries Report, bazi remubatanidzwa wenyika dzose rinoona nezvekutengeserana nebudiriro reUN Conference on Trade and Development kana kuti UNCTAD rinoti nyika idzi dzinofanirwa kushanduro hwaro nemamiriro ezvehupfumi hwadzo kuti dzvizvipukunyutse kubva "pachikirimbani chehurombo"- icho chiri kumisa kukura nekubudirira pazvehupfumi.
Pakati penyika makumi mana nesere dzinonzi neU.N. ndidzo dzisina kubudirira zvachose kudarika dzimwe nyika, kana kuti "Least Developed Countries" (LDCs), panongova neimwe chete, nyika ye Laos, iri mugwara kuti ikunde pazviga zvinomwe zvebudiriro kana kuti Millennium Development Goals (MDG's) panozosvika gore ra2015.
Nyika ina dzoga muAfrica dzinoti Ethiopia, Malawi, Rwanda and Uganda ndidzo dzingangokwanisa kuzadzikisa zvizhinji zvezviga izvi.
Ongororo iyi irikubva yaunza rima nekuda kwezvimwe zvidenho zvakatarisana nyika idzi mumakore ari kumberi
Zviga zvema MDGs zvakapa chinangwa kunyika kuti dzidambure nepakati zviyero zvehurombo hwadzo panosvika gore ra2015.
Zvimwe zviga zvebudiriro inogona kuzadzikisika kana kuti Sustainable Development Goals, izvo zvonoendera mberi nebasa rinenge rasiiwa nema MDGs, zvinodanidzirawo kuti hurombo hunge hwaparadzwa nekupedzwa panozosvika gore ra 2030.
Semaonero aTaffere Tesfachew, mubati webasa muUNCTAD anoshanda nenyika dzemuAfrica, zvinotoda chishamiso choga kuti ndudzi dzisina kubudirira kudarika dzimwe kana kuti ma LDCs dzikunde apa.
Kuti nyika dzine budiriro shomanana kudarika dzimwe dzigone kuita chishamiso ichi, anoti dzinofanirwa dzinofanirwa kushandura mamiriro nemashandiro anoita zvehupfumi hwadzo.
Anoudza VOA kuti izvi zvinoreva kubvisa vashandi kubva kumabasa anounza pundutso shoma, zvakaita sekurima patwuminda twudoko nemabasa vachienda kumabasa anounza pundutso nekukasira akaita sekugadzira zvinhu nemidziyo nekushanda mabasa anokosheswa nevanhu.
Nyika dziri kukwirira ndedziya dziri kusika mikana kune vaye vava kusiya zvekurima vachiita mamwe mabasa anowedzera hukoshi hwezvigadzirwa, uko vari kuwana kudzidziswa kwekushanda nemaoko, uye pazvinoitika izvi bazi rezvekugadzira zvinhu rine chinhu ichi, ndokusaka paine kukurudzira panyaya yekugadzira zvinhu, akadaro
"Nyika dziri kushandisa hwaro hwekushanda kwehurumende dzadzo kuti dzifambise nekukonzera mari nevashandi kuti vapinda muchikamu ichi dziri kuita zviri nani."
Tesfachew anoti zvikamu izvi zvinoburitsa zvigadzirwa zvakawanda zvinopawo mihoro yepamusoro uye inosika mukana wekuti pave nekuda kutengwa kwezvigadzirwa zvazvo.
Anoti izvi zvinokurudzira nekukoka kuuya kwemari inopfimbikwa mumamabhindauko nemabhizimisi.
Zvichitariswa nepanze, zvinoita sekuti nyika dziri muchikwata chema LDCs hadzisi kuita zvakanyanya kuipa hadzo.
Hwerengedzo yeUNCTAD pane ruzivo rwezvirikuitika mune zvehupfumi munyika rombo idzi pakati pa2002 na2008 yakadarika chiga chezvikamu zvinomwe muzana chakanganchatarwa nenyika dzepasi rose.
Uye kunyangwe mushure memhirizhonga yezvehupfumi yemugore ra2008, UNCTAD inoti nyika dziri muboka remaLDCs dzakakura nekukasira kudarika dzimwebnyika dzichiri kusimukira, dziri pachiyero chezvikamu zvishanu zvine chidimbu chinomwe kubva muzana pagore.
Asi nyanzvi dzezvehupfumi dzeU.N. dzinoti remangwana renyika dzisina kubudirira kudarika dzimwe dzese munguva iri pedyo pedyo nenguva nenguva iri pakati nepakati inouya rinoramba risina kujeka.
Nyanzvi idzi dzinoti kuwedzera goneso yevanhu kuti vasike nekugadzira zvinhu ndiyo nzira yakanakisisa yekutyora tsika zvekushaikwa kana kudopoka kwebudiriro yevanhu nezvehupfumi kunovabata muriva rehurombo.
UN Inoti: Nyika Zhinji DzemuAfrica Dzichapotsa Zviga Zvebudiriro kana kuti Ma MDG Zvegore ra2015
Nyika Zhinji DzemuAfrica Dzichapotsa Zviga Zvebudiriro kana kuti Ma MDG Zvegore zvakatemerwa gore ra2015 nekuda kwemukaha uripo pakati pe budiriro yezvehupfumi nebudiriro iri muvanhu.
Ichi ndicho chimwe chezvinhu chakabuda muchinyorwa cheongororo netsvakurudzo chegore pamusoro penyika dzine budiriro shomanana kudarika dzimwe dzose kana kuti Least Developed Countries (LCDs), chakaturwa nemusi weChina.
Junior Davis, mushandi weU.N. anoona nezvehupfumi muAfrica, akati nyika dzemuAfrica hadzina kunge dzichikwanisa kushandura kukura kwezvehupfumi hwadzo kuti huburitse kukura neshanduko yezvinhu zvinobatika zvadzinenge dzavaka.
Tinofunga kuti ndizvo zviri kuitika nekuti nyika ridzi hadzina kunangisa zvakakwana pakuvaka zvatinodaidza kuti goneso yavo yekushanda zvine pundutso, akadaro Davis.
"Idzi igoneso dzinofanirwa kuvepo dzebudiriro yevanhu nepane zvehupfumi dzinodiwa kuti dziunze budiriro mune zvehupfumi inochengeteka kuti irambe ichiendera mberi. Uye maMDG, semagadzirirwo aakaitwa, kazhinji akange asine hanya nekuvaka goneso dzekushanda zvinopa pundutso."
Budiriro iri kunonoka
Nyika dzemu Africa hadzisi zvakare munzira yekudambura nepakati huwandu nehudzamu hwehurombo panosvika gore ra2015, uye budiriro yadzo pakuderedza nzara iri kunonoka.
Hurombo hunoderedza kusimukira kwevanhu uye kunokanganisa goneso yekushanda zvine pundutso.
Uyewo budiriro yezvehupfumi inodikanwa kuti pave nechimuko panezvekubudirira kwevanhu.
Ethiopia, Rwanda, Uganda neMalawi ndidzo chete nyika adziri mugwara rekuzadzikisa zvizhinji zvezvinangwa zvebudiriro izvi.
Dziri kufambira mberi nekuti dzakaisa mari zhinji muzvikamu zvinounza budiriro inoenderera mberi yakaita sezvivakwa, hutano nezvekudzidza.
Hurongwa hwebudiriro mushure megore ra 2015 kuitira nyika ndonda umo kutonga nekutungamirira zvichiri matambudziko dzakaita seSouth Sudan neDemocratic Republic of Congo hucharangwa hwakazembera parubatsiro rwekune dzimwe nyika dzepasi rose kuti dzigone kuva nebudiriro yemumagariro evanhu nepane zvehupfumi, Davis akadaro.
Kukwidziridza budiriro mumaruwa, kuwedzera zvinobuda nepundutso mumakambani anogadzira zvinhu nemidziyo, zvekurima uye nemapoka ezvehupfumo anoita basa rekupa nekubatsira vanhu zvinhu zvavanoda nekushandisa misi nenguva zviri munyika idzi zvichada "nzira dzekuti panenge paine gwara rekukura nekusimukira risingangoratidze kuti rinogara riripo asiwo rinounza mabasa nazhinji," Davis akadaro.
"Nekuti tinoona budiriro mumabasa uye kuwana basa kwakakosha chaizvo pahurongwa hupi zvahwo hungavepo hwekuderedza hurombo nenzira inogara iripo."
Nyika inozoiswa pachikwata chenyika dzine budiriro shomanana kudarika dzimwe, kana kuti Least Developed Countries mari inowanikwa nemunhu wega wega, hutera hwezvehupfumi, uye zvinonongedzera kusimukira kwevanhu zvakaita sehutano nechikafu chavanodya.
Panyika makumi mana nesere dzenyika dzisina kubudirira kudarika dzimwe dzese, nyika makumi matatu neina dziri muAfrica.
Nyika nhatu dzakayambuka kubva muchinzvimbo chekuva nyika dzisina kubudirira zvachose dzinoti: Botswana, Cape Verde neSamoa.
Kuramwa Basa Kwevashandi kunogarisa pasi mabasa ezvemutemo muMalawi
Kuramwa basa kwesvondo rose nevashandi vanotsigira bazi rezvemutemo muMalawi kwagarisa pasi matare edzimhosva, zvakonzera kuzarisa kwemastokisi anochengeterwa vabatwa pamalamba emapurisa uye nekumiswa pasina anoziva kuti kusvikira rinhi kwekutongwa kwenyaya hombe,- kusanganisira kutongwa kwevashandi vehurumende munyaya dzehuori.
Vanochengetedza hurongwa pamatare edzimhosva, vanyori nezvikonzi vari kuda kuwedzerwa kwemihoro yavo nezvikamu makumi matatu kubva muzana pamari yavari kutambira ikezvino sekuvumbisa kwehurumende makore maviri akadarika.
Kudanhidzira nekuimba pazvivanze zvematare edzimhosva ndizvo zvava kuvaraidza vashandi vari kuramwa mabasa ava kubva pakatanga chirongwa chekuuya kubasa asi vasingashande svondo rakapera.
Linley Hebert, mutauriri wevashandi vari kuramwa mabasa ava, akaudza VOA kuti kuramwa mabasa uku kuri kubva pakukonewa kwehurumende kuzadzikisa zvayakawirorana nevashandi vayo muna 2012.
Muna Gumiguru gore rino, hurumende yakasimudzira mihoro yevashandi vehurumende, asi isu hatina iswawo pakati pevakawedzerwa mihoro yavo, Hebert akadaro.
Asi muna 2012, takaita chibvumirano chekuti nguva yese pavawedzera mihoro yevashandi vehurumende, vanobva vawedzerawo neyedu mihoro.
Saka (mushure mekuzembera nekuremekedza chibvumirano chemuna 2013), tiri kushamiswa kuona kuti rwendo rwuno takabva tasiiwa tiri kunze.
Vakuru vehurumende vanoti kukonewa kuwedzera mari dzemihoro dvevashandi vemubazi rezvemutemo gore rino zvakanyanyokonzerwa nekuoma pane zvemari, mushure mekumiswa kwemari yaibva kumasangano anobatsira ichipihwa hurumende yeMalawi.
Kumiswa kwekuwedzerwa kwemari uku kuri kubva pahuori hwezvemari umo mari inodarika mamiriyoni makumi matatu yakamoorwa kubva muhomwe dzehurumende
Mutariri webazi rezvehupfumi, Nations Msowoya akaudza nhepfenyuro yemunharaunda kuti zvakaomera hurumede kuti izadzikise zviri kudiwa nevashandi vayo.
Zvakaoma kuvimbisa kuti vabati vechikwama chehurumende vachaita chii.
Asi regai ndingoti mamiriro ezvehupfumi nekusomeka kwemari yekushandisa yehurumende zvichaita kuti zviite sekugozhera vabati vechikwama chehurumende kuti vaite zviri kudiwa nevashandi, "Msowoya akadaro.
Asi nemaonero aHebert, vashandi ava havasi kuzodzokera kubasa kusvikira zvavari kuda zvadzikiswa.
"Kubva zvandakazvarwa hapana nguva yekuti hurumende yaiti ine mari".
Ine nzira yayo (yekuwana mari iyi) uye ichawana nzira yekutipa mari iyi, Herbert akasimbirira kudaro.
Kuramwa mabasa kuri kuenderera mberi uku kuri kukanganisa kufambira mberi kwekutongwa kwenyaya, sezvo mabasa ematare edzimhosva akambomiswa kushanda.
Kutongwa kwakawanda kwevanhu, kusanganisira kweuya akambove gurukota rezvemutemo, Ralph Kasambara, ari kupomerwa mhosva yekuva chikamu chehuori hwemari yakabiwa, kwakamiswa svondo rakapera pasina anoziva kuti kusvikira rinhi.
Mapurisa ari kugunun'una kuti mastokisi mavanochengetra vanhu vari kunenedzerwa mhosva vasati vaenda kunotongwa makazarisa nekuti hapana vanhu vari kuendeswa kumatare.
Mutauriri wemapurisa emuMalawi Rhoda Manjolo akaudza VOA imwe nzira yavasara nayo "ndeyekuti vanhu vae mhosva diki vatongwe vachibva kudzimba dzavo."
Vanorwira nekukurudzira kodzero dzevanhu nenyanzvi dzemutemo vanoti kuramwa mabasa uku kuri kuwedzera pakutyorwa kwemitemo yevanhu.
Kune vanhu vanofanirwa kuendeswa kunotongwa kumatare edzimhisva maawa makumi mana nemasere asati adarika, rakadaro gweta, George Kadzipatike, rinoshanda mukambani yemagweta muguta rekumaodzanyenba enyika rinonzi Mzuzu.
"Hatisi kugona kunyora tsamba tichivakumbirira kuti vatongwe vachibva kudzimba dzavo.
Kune vaye vanhu vasisade kugara nevavakawanana navo, uye vari kuda kuti matare edzimhosva avati varambana zviri pamutemo, asi hatisi kugona kunyora chikumbiro chakadai kuburikidza nematare."
Vanhu vane zvigaro muhurumende vanoti nhaurirano dzemuchivande kuti nyaya iyi igadzirike dziri kuenderera mberi muguta guru, Lilongwe.
Asi vashandi vari kuramwa mabasa vakaudza VOA kuti kunyangwe zvikaendepi, havasi kuzogamuchira kuwedzerwa kwemihoro yavo kuri pasi pezvikamu makumi matatu kubva muzana.
Kuramwa mabasa kwakafanana nekuku kwaita mwedzi mitatu muna2012 mushure mekunge vatongi vematare epasi neepamusoro vose vapindawo mukuramwa mabasa uku.
Zhara kuchamhembe kweAfrica Yakashatisisa Kudarika Zvakange Zvichitarisirwa
Bandiko remubatanidzwa wenyika dzepasi rose rinoona nezvekuwanikwa kwekudya kuvanhu vari mumatambudziko reUnited Nations World Food Program, kana kuti WFP, rinoti zhara kuchamhembe kweAfrica yakanyanya kuipa kudarika zvakange zvichitarisirwa.
Vakuru veWFP vari kuyambira kuti vanhu vanosvika mamiriyoni gumi nematatu munyika nhanhatu dzinoti: Malawi, Zambia, Lesotho, Zimbabwe, Swaziland neMozambique vari munjodzi yekufa nezhara kana vakasabatsirwa nezvekudya.
Vakuru veWorld Food Program vanoti vanoda chikafu chinoyera matani miriyoni rimwe chete kuti chirerutse zhara kuchamhembe kweAfrica, asi havana chokwadi kuti vachachiwana chikafu ichi.
Muchikumbiro kunyika dzepasi rose chakaitwa muutanga kwaChikunguru, vakuru veWFP vakakumbira mari ingasvike mazana mazana mashanu emamiriyoni emadhora ekutenga chikafu.
Pari zvino vakwanisa kuwana zvikamu makumi maviri kubva muzana kwemari iyi. Mukuru weWFP kuchemhembe kweAfrica, Judith Lewis, anoti mamiriro ezvinhu asvika kumawere chaiko pekuti voshaiwa zano.
