"Mukana wekuti tinzvenge nyatwa muvanhu wavakuvharika," akadaro.
"Tinoda rubetsero rwakawanda ikezvino.
Tinoda kui chikafu chinge chava muzvikepe munyanza chichiuya kuno, kana kuti tinoda mari yekutenga zvinodiwa zvichiri kuwanikwa kuchamhembe kweAfrica, kuti tinzvenge ruhavashava rwukuru urwu."
Pari zvino, the WFP iri kubatsira mamiriyoni matanhatu evanhu vari panjodzi yakaipisisa munyika nhanhatu dzakanyanya kubatwa nedambudziko rezhara iri.
Chikamu chiri pakati nepakati chevanhu ava vari muZimbabwe.
Bandiko iri rinoti rine idi yekuti kuwandu hwevanhu vachada ruyamuro rwuchawedzera.
Sangano rezvehutano pasi pose reWorld Health Organization rinoti dunhu rekuchamhembe kweAfrica, pamusoro pekuva nehuwandu hwekupararira kwedende reshuramatongo pasi rose, ndirowo rine huwandu hwakakurisisa pasi rose rwevanhu vanorwara nekusadya kudya kunovaka muviri.
Sangano iri rinotarisira kuti vanhu vangasvike zviuru mazana matatu vangangofa mumwedzi mitanhatu inotevera nekudakwezvirwere zvine chekuita nekushaiwa kudya kwakanaka kunovaka muviri.
Muzvare Lewis vanoto kwatotanga kufiwa.
"Tiri kuona vanhu vachibva kumisha yavo," akadaro.
"Kana vakaziva kuti pachazove nekugoverwa kwechikafu, vanobva vatoenda ikoko pasina kupedza nguva.
Dambudziko nderekuti hatitorina chikafu chinoringana kuvanhu vakanyorwa pasi kuti vapihwe chikafu ichi, tisingataure nezvevamwe vanhu vari mune dzimwe nzvimbo. Pangaite mukana wekuti panopedzesera pava nemhirizhonga here? Hongu. "
Judith Lewis weWFP anoti panguva ino yegore bandiko iri rinenge richironga kuti rinowana sei chikafu chinopinda mudunhu iri mvura isati yaturuka muzhizha munaGumiguru.
Asi vanoti sezvo WFP yatova nedambudziko kuzadzikisa zviga zvayo zvaitori nazvo, hangakwanise kuchitanga kurongera kuunzwa kwechikafu chichazoda kushandiswa kumberi uko.
Mutungamiriri weCanada Anofadzwa nehurongwa hwebudiriro hwemuAfrica
Mutungamiriri weCanada, Jean Chretien anoti ari kufadzwa nekufambira mberi kuri kuita basa rekumisa hurongwa hwekubudirira kweAfrica.
Chretien akataura mashoko aya neSvondo mushure mekusangana nemutungamiriri weSouth Africa vaThabo Mbeki vevamwe vatungamiriri vedunhu reAfrica iri muPretoria.
Chretien, anova sachigaro wechikwata chenyika nomwe dzakabudirira kudarika dzimwe, kuchiwedzerwa Russia, ari kushanyira Africa kuti aite nhaurirano pamuso pe Kushandirapamwe Kutsva Kuitira Kubudirira KweAfrica kana kuti New Partnership for Africa's Development, inowanzozivikanwa sekuti NEPAD.
Akati NEPAD ichange iri imwe yamadonzvo epamusoro soro pamusangano wenyika dzakabudirira kudarika dzimwe unonzi G-8 ku Kananaskis, Canada, muna Chivabvu.
Nyika dziri muG-8 dzinoti Britain, Canada, France, Germany, Italy, Japan, the United States neRussia.
Chretien anoti misoro yenyaya dzakaita kodzero dzevanhu, gutsaruzhinji, simba remutemo pakugadzirisa nyaya munyika, kujeka zvisina kuvanza nehunjari njari uyewo nekutonga kwakanaka zvichataurwa nezvazvo pamusangano mukuru uyu weG8.
NEPAD inojekesa zviga zvekukurudzira gutsaruzhinji nekutonga kwakanaka muAfrica kuti iwane rubatsiro rwezvehupfumi kubva kunyika dzekumavirira.
Ine chinangwa chekuwanakukura pagore kwezvikamu zvinomwe kubva muzana munyika dzose dzemuAfrica panosvika gore ra2015.
Mutungamiriri weSouth Africa vaMbeki vakapwiswa kuti Africa yagadzira NEPAD vachitiwo panga paine kufambira mberi panyaya yegutsaruzhinji muAfrica.
Mushure mezvizvi, Chretien navaMbeki vakazobatanawo nevatungamiriri Festus Mogae vekuBotswana, Bakili Muluzu veMalawi, Joaquim Chissano vekuMozambique, Sam Nujoma vekuNamibia, Benjamin Makapa vekuTanzania nemutevedzeri wemutungamiriri weZambia Enoch Kavindele.
Mutungamiriri weZimbabwe vaRobert Mugabe, avo vakakunda pasarudzo dzakaitwa kepiri mwedzi wadkadarika asi zviri kurambwa nemapato anokwikwidza, havana kukokwa.
Sangano frenhau reReuters rinonyora nhau pamusoro pemutungamiriri weCanada uyo atoshanyira Morocco, Algeria neNigeria parwendo rwake kunyika nhanhatu, achashanyirawo Ethiopia neSenegal mushure meSouth Africa.
Zvimwe zvinyorwa munhau idzi zvakapihwa neReuters neAFP.
Kushandiswa Kwevana Mukuita Mabasa Evanhu Vakuru MuMalawi
Sangano rinonzi Ziso Remwana kana kuti, Eye of the Child, riri kuratidza kushushikana pamusoro pezvarinoti vana vakawanda vari kumanikidzwa kushanda nekuda kwehurombo.
Inoti vana ava vari munjodzi yekubatwa zvisina kunaka nekukanganiswa nevanhu vakuru.
Vamwe vana vane mazera madoko chose vanoshanda vachisheedzera kuti vanhu vakwire michovha mudunhu rinoitwa zvemabhizimisi ekutenga nekutengesa reLimbe muguta guru muMalawi munezvekutenga nekutengesa, Blantyre.
Ava ndivo vamwe vevana varikusundwa nekumanikidzwa kutsvaga mabasa nekuda kwehurombo.
Maxwell Matewere ndiye mukuru anofambisa basa reEye of the Child.
Anoti vana vazhinji vanobva kumaruwa
Anoti, "Ikezvino hatisati taita ongoro yekuona hwuwandu asi bazi rinoona nezvemabasa rine hurongwa hwekuita izvi nekukasira richibatsirwa nemari kubva kuInternational Labor Organization.
Asi tichishandisa ongororo yedu uye kuburikidza nemabasa edu, tinofunga kuti kushanda kwevana vachiita mabasa evanhu vakuru idambudziko guru chose zvikuru sei kumaruwa, uye unogona kuzviona nekufambiswa kwevana zviri kunze kwemutemo kubva kumaruwa vachiendeswa kumaguta uko vazhinji vevana ava vari kushanda mudzimba dzevanhu.
VaMatewere vanoti vana varombo vanowanzowana basa pamapurazi makuru.
Takaonawo zvinoratidzo kuti kune vana vari kushanda mumapurazi makuru etii neefodya.
Kune vana zvakare vari kushanda mukuforoma zvidhinha, uye kazhinji vabereki vavo ndivo vanoronga kuti vapinde mumabasa akadai. "
VaMatewere vanoti the Eye of the Child yava nehumboo hwekuti pane kutyorwa kukuru kwekodzero dzevana munyika,
Izvi zvinosanganisira kubatwa chibharo, kubatwa nekushandiswa kwemiviri yavo zvisina kunaka nekushandiswa zvisina mwero.
Vanoti izvi zvinotyora zvisungo zvemubatanidzwa wenyika dzose pamusoro pekodzero dzevana, kana kuti United Nations Convention on the Rights of the Child.
Vakati kana ukatarisa Convention of the Rights of a Child, "uchaona kuti inopa kuchengetedzwa kwevana kubva pakushandiswa kusina kunaka muzvinhu zvese nemabasa ose anokuvadza kana kukanganisa hutano hwavo kana kukura kwavo kwakanaka izviwo zvichizokanganisa kugona kwavo kudzidza.
Saka vana vari kuwanikwa vachishanda mumapurazi makuru anorima tii, vanowanikwa vachiforoma zvidhinha, zviri pachena kuti kodzero dzavo zvezvadzakatarwa muConvention for the Rights of the Children uyewo nemubumbiro remutemo dziri kutyorwa. "
Mukuru anoona nezvekufambiswa kwebasa pa The Eye of the Child anoti sangano ravo riri kutarisa nzira dzekuchengetedza kodzero dzemwana.
Vanoti kuti izvi zvogoneke, chikwata chavo chakatotanga kuita zvirongwa zvakati kuti.
"Tichangotanga chirongwa chitsva uye zvatiri kuedza kuita kuudza veruzhinji nezvezvinhu zvanoita kuti hupenyu hwevana huenderere mberi zvakanaka uye nekuvaudza nezvekodzero dzevana.
Panguva imwe chete tiri kudawo kuvaka goneso yevana pachezvavo kuti zvichida vanogona kushandisa izwi ravo rinorevesa kuti vataure pachena zvinhu zvinovashungurudza nekuvanetsa."
Sekutaurwa kwazvakaitwa nevakuru mubandiko rehurumende chinoona nezvemabasa, vana vazhinji vanomakidzwa kusiya chokoro votsvaga basa nekuti vabereki vavo havakwanise kuvabhadharira mari kuti vaende kuchikoro.
Kunyangwe hazvo kudzidza kuzvidanho zvekutanga muzvikoro zvemuMalawi kuri kwemahara, vana vazhinji havaende nekuti vanenge vachishaiwa zvimwewo zvinhu zvinodikanwa muhupenyu, zvakaita senhumbi.
Chikamu chinodarika makumi matanhatu kubva muzana chemamiriyoni angasvike gumi nerimwe evanhu vemuMalawi vanorarama muhurombo huri pasi pechiyero chinoita kuti vanhu vangopona zvezuva nezuva.
Dare Remhosva RemuMalawi Rinowana Vanhu Gumi Nemumwe Vine Mhosva Yekukuuraya Vasope
Dare guru remuMalawi rakawana vanhu vashanu, kusanganisira mukoma wemushakabvu, vaine mhosva yakaitwa muna2018 yekuponda murume musope wemakore makumi maviri nemaviri.
Dare iri rakawana vamwe vanhu vanomwe vaine mhosva yekutengesa mitezo yemurume musope akapondwa uyu.
Vakuru vemuMalawi vanoti vasope vanodarika zana nemakumi manomwe vakapondwa munyika kubva muna 2014 nevanhu vanofunga kuti mitezo yavo inounza rombo rakanaka nehupfumi.
Hama dzemushakabvu, MacDonald Masambuka, dzakabuda muimba yekutongwa yedare dziine tariro yekuti kutonga kwekururamisira kuchaitwa mushure mekunge dare rawana vanhu vose gumi nevaviri vari kupomerwa mhosva vaine mhosva yekumuponda.
Nhengo dzemhuri, dzaisanganisira amai vaMasambuka, vairatidza kudzikama apo mutongi Dorothy NyaKaunda Kamanga aiverenga mitongo yake.
Vakawanikwa vaine mhosva vanosanganisira fata wechechi yeRoma, Father Thomas Muhosa, mupurisa Chikondi Chileka, mushandi wepachipatara Lumbani Kamanga, uye nemukoma wemushakabvu, Cassim Masambuka.
Mhosva dzavo dzaisanganisira kuponda, kubvisa mitezo kubva pamuviri wemunhu kuunza kukuvadza kumuviri wemunhu anorarama nehurema nekuba nekufambisa vanhu zviri kunze kwemutemo.
Kamanga akawana mukoma wemushakabvu nevamwe vana vaine mhosva yekumuponda.
Dare rakawana vamwe vanomwe, kusanganisira fata nemupurisa, vaine mhosva yekutengesa mitezo yemushakabvu.
Kuita mari nekutengesa mitezo. Maringe nezvakataurwa nedare, Muhosha, Chileka nevamwe vakati vaigona kuita mhindu vachishandisa mitezo yakabviswa pachitunha chemunhu.
Mutongi akati vachuchuti vakaratidza humboo husina kupokana kuti vanhu gumi nevaviri ava vakarangana kuuraya Masambuka nekuzobvisa mapfupa ake kubva pamuviri wake vachifungidzira kuti vaizobatsirikana nekuwana mari.
Akati Masambuka ndiye munhu achangobva mukupondwa kuburikidza nekukuvadzwa zvakaipisisa kwevanhu vanorarama nehusope vanga vasiri kuchengetedzwa nekurwirwa nevanhu vagere munharaunda.
Mukuru wevachuchuti Steve Kayuni ndiye akange akamiririra hurumende mumhosva iyi.
Akati akafadzwa kuti dare rakatenderana naye pamhosva dzose dzaakatura kudare achiti ndidzo dzakange dzaparwa.
Chinhu chinobitirira kurutivi rwehurumende kuti kana ukazvitarisisa kuti munyayaya iyi muna fata arimo, mune muprisa arimowo uye muene mukoma wemushakabvu ari mukati mayo zvakare.
Ukatarisisa, inotenderera pachinzvimbo chekuvimbwa zvekuti munhu akaita samushakabvu Macdonald Masambuka aivimba nevanhu ava zvekuti, ndivo vakazopedzesera vomurasisa nekumutengesa, Kayuni akadaro.
Masambuka akatanga kushaikwa kubva mumusha wake musi wa 9 Kurume, 2018, uye muviri wake wakange usisina maoko nemakumbo wakazowanikwa wakavigwa mubindu musi wa 2 Kubvumbi, 2018, mudunhu raaigara reMachinga kuchamhembe kweMalawi.
Kurunzirwa Mapepa emudare redzimhosva anoratidza kuti Masambuka akarunzirwa nemukoma wake kuti asangane neshamwari dzake, vaiti vakange vamuwanira musikana wekuti aroore.
Asi pavasvika panzvimbo yakazoparwa mhosva, dziya dzainzi ishamwari dzakabva dzabata nechisimba Masambuka nepamutsipa, ndokumuzvuvira kubindu uko vakasvikomuurayira.
Ipapo, vapondi vake vakacheka maoko nemakumbo ake, ndokupisa muviri wake vachishandisa mafuta epeturu ndokumuviga ipapo.
Iyi ndiyo nyaya yekutanga ine vanhu vanozivikanwa zvikuru munharaunda vachiwanikwa vari mukati mekuponda vanhu vanorarama nehusope.
Masauko Chamkakala, gweta revapomerwi gumi nevaviri ava munyaya iyi rakati raizowana zvekutaura pamusoro penyaya iyi kana awana nguva yekurava mutongo uyu.
Tichakamirira kuti tione chinyorwa chekutongwa chapepetwa kuti tichiverenge nekuchinzvera, tozotaura nevanhu vatanga tichimiririra munyaya iyi, Chamkakala akadaro.
Vanhu vanorwira kodzero vakati vaitarisira dare kuti ripe mutongo unorwadza chose kuna avo vese vakawanikwa vaine mhosva.
Mutongo usina jee'
Ian Simbota wakange akamirira musangano wevanhu vanorarama nehusope cheAssociation of Persons with Albinism padare.
Mutongi paanga achiverenga, chandibata chikamu chiya apo fata weRoma, Father Muhosha nevamwe vawanikwa vaine mhosva yekutengesa mitezo yemuviri wemunhu.
Kana ukanorava mutemo pamusoro pemitezo yemumuviri wemunhu, Anatomy Act, hazvina kuoma kuti uone nekunzwisisa kutyorwa kwemutemo pakadai.
Saka takanyatsomirira kuti tione kuti mutongi, kana zvichigoneka, kuti aone nyaya iyi sekubata nekurwadza kwairi kuita vanhu, nekuti tinofanirwa kuti tione mutongo unorema usina jee panyaya iyi, akadaro, Simbota.
Dare repamusoro riri kutarisirwa kutura mutongo waro pamhondi idzi musi wa 30 Chivabvu.
Mune imwe nyaya, nemusi weChina, dare repamusoro rakatongera mumwe murume ane makore makumi matatu nemanomwe kugara muchitoro mukomana wemakore gumi nemana airarama nehusope mudunhu rePhalombe.
Mushandi mukuru muhurumende yeZimbabwe Anotsigira Kutsikirirwa Pasi Kwekuratidzira, Anokurudzira Moyo Murefu Pane Zvehupfumi.
Gurukota rinoona nezvekunze kweZimbabwe nekutengeserana nedzimwe nyika nemusi weMuvhuro vakatsigira kutsikirirwa pasi kwekuratidzira kwekushora hurumende rikakurudzira kuti paitwe moyo murefu mukuvandudza kwezvehupfumi hwenyika hwurikudzadzarika.
Kunyangwe hazvo "munhu wese anekodzero yekuratidzira,"panga pavakuita zevezeve nekukurudzira mhirizhonga," Sibusiso B. Moyo vakaudza told VOA munhaurirano yekubvunzwa mibvunzo.
Achitaura nezvekuchengetedzwa kweveruzhinji, akadzigira mutongo wedare redzimhosva rwakasimbisa kumiswa nemapurisa kwekuratidzira kwakange kwarongwa nesangano rinopikisa reMovement for Democratic Change (MDC) alliance.
Vatungamiriri veAlliance vari kusunda mutungamiriri wenyika vaEmmerson Mnangagwa nebato rir kutonga reZANU-PF kuti ikwanewo muhurumende ichambobata matomu ichiyambutsa nyika kubva pairi kusvikira zvinhu zvadzikama.
Vakange varonga kuratidzira musi weMuvhuro muBulawayo, guta rechipiri pakukura munyika, asi vakuru vemapurisa vakakudzivisa kwasara maawa mashoma kuti kutange.
Kumwe kuratidzira kuviri kuchakaronga svondo rino: kweguta riri pakati oenyika reGweru neChipiri uye nekweguta riri kuchamhembe kwakadziva kumabvazuva enyika reMasvingo neChitatu.
Mapurisa akange atofanodzivisa kuratidzira uku, chinhu chakazotsigirwawo nedare redzimhosva remuZimbabwe.
Mazana evatsigiri veMDC vakashaiwa hanya nekudziviswa uku, zvakazoita kuti pave nekudhumana pakati pevagari nemapurisa.
Mifananidzo yezvivhitivhiti nemufananidzo nje yairatidza mapurisa achirova nekukava vamwe varatidziri pakati pezvimwe zvavayiita izvo zvakaita kuti pave nekugunun'una kubva kumapoka anomiririra vagari neanorwira kodzero dzevanhu kusanganisira hofisi yezvekodzero dzevanhu yeUnited Nations kwekuti mapurisa akashandisa simba rakawandisisa pakuedza kudzivisa vairatidzira.
Mapurisa, kwete vanhu vairatidzira, ndivo vakauya vakapakatira zvombo mumigwagwa yemuBulawayo neMuvhuro, vaine napurisa ayifamba netsoka vaine zvinhu zvekuzvichengetedza kana vakatemwa nematombo nezvimwe, uye vaine tsvimbo zvakare vamwe vavo vaine zvivhorovhoro.
Sangano renhau reAssociated Press rakatura nhau dzekuti motokari huru dzemapurisa nedzimwe dzinomwaya mvura inovava dzakange dzakamiswa munzvimbo dzemuguta dzinofamba nekutengwa neveruzhinji.
Mumwe murume wechidiki wemuBulawayo, akazviti anongonzi James, akaudza VOA kuti kutaurirana nekuwirirana pakati pehurumende nevakuru vemapato anokwikwidza dzakange dzakakosha kudarika kuratidzira uku.
Kutaura chokwadi, kana tikaratidzira, tinogona kupedzisira takuvadzwa nekurohwa, nekudzingirirwa.
Hapana chisvinu chatinoona chichibuda pazviri, James akadaro.
"Asi varume ava vanofanirwa kugara pasi voona kuti chii chaizvo chavanogona kutiitira, zvikuru sei isu, vechidiki. Takakanganiswa zvakanyanya, uye tavakutochembera tichingomhanya."
Moyo, gurukota rezvekunze, akaudza VOA kuti hurumende iri "kurongedza nekugadzirisa shanduko pane zvehupfumi zvinova hwaro nenheyo uye zviri tsvongonoro dzekuona kuti kunyangwe vechidiki vanozopedzeserawo vawana mabasa avanenge vagadzirirwa, kuitira kuti tigadzire mamiriro ezvinhu ekuti vanoda kuita mabhizimisi munyika uye nemari dzacho vanozviwana zviri nyore muuya munyika, mabasa ozogadzirwa, uyewo vechidiki vovawo chikamu nechidimbu chezvinenge zvichiitika mune zvehupfumi."
Moyo akati Zimbabwe vava pakati nepakati pagwendo gwemakore maviri "gwehurongwa gwekudzikamisa zvingu panguva yekuyambuka kubva mune zvazuro" gwekumutsiridza zvehupfumi hwenyika zvakashakadzwa: "Tasara negore rimwe kuti tipedze gwendo gwedu, uye titi kuti panhambo idzodzo tinenenge tabuda mumatope ati maari aya."
Nyika iyi iri kuchamhembe kweAfrica iine vanhu vangapotse vasvike ,amiriyoni gumi nematanhatu iri mudope rakaipisisa mune zvemari zvisati zvamboitika kubva gore ra2008, zvakonzerwa nekukwira kwemitengo kuri kukonzerwa nekudonha kwehukoshi hwemari yemunyika nekusakadzwa kwakakonzerwa nemakore nemakore ehuvori munyika.
Vanhu vakawanda vanotambura kutenga zvinhu zvinodiwa zuva nezuva, zvakaita semishonga nezvekudya.
Mukati mezvehupfumi hwakaromboka, zvirimwa zvakatsvaigwa nekushaikwa kwemvura vuye nemadutuemvura yakawandisa, bazi reUN reWorld Food Program rinotarisira kuti vanhu vanosvika mamiriyoni mashanu nezviuru mazana mashanu zvichada zvekudya nekukasira Kubvumbi wegore rinouya asati asvika.
Gurukota rezvemari,Mthuli Ncube, uyo akange atarisira kuti hupfumi hwaizokura nezvikamu zvitatu nechidimbu chimwe chete mugore ra2019, akazouya nezviri kunystoitika zvinochangamutsa kudare reparamende yeZimbabwe pakutanga kwaNyamavhuvhu.
"Ongororo itsva yezvichaitika muna2019 inoratidza kuti pachange pasina kukura kwezvirikuitika munezvehupfumi," Sangano renhau reReuters rakanyora nhau dzaro richiti ndizvo zvaakange ataura.
Ncube haana kupa humwe humboo hunoratidza kuwanda kana kudzikira pane zvehupfumi.
Vashandi Vemasangano Anorwira Kodzero Dzevanhu Vanonetswa Nevanoona Nezvekuchengetedzwa KweTanzania, Zvichiratidza Kuwedzerwa Kwekutsikira
Varwiri dzekodzero dzevagari vemuAfrica vari kumusangano mukuru uri kuitirwa kuTanzania vakabvunzurudzwa vakayambirwa pakupera kwesvondo, muchiitiko chiri kunzi nevarwiri vekodzero dzevanhu chikamu chiri kuenderera mberi chekutsikirira pasi rusunguko rwekuti vanhu vanogona kutaura zvavanoda nekufunga vakasununguka.
Zvichiri kubuda zvishoma nezvishoma zvekuti chii chaizvo chakanyatsoitika kuvashandi vasiri pasi pemakumi mana vemasangano anorwira kodzero dzevagari vakanetsana nevashandi vanoona nezvekuchengetedzwa nerunyararo munyika pamusangano mukuru wemubatanidzwa dzenyika dzekuchamhembe kweAfrica unonzi Southern African Development Community wakaitirwa muDar es Salaam.
Asi nyanzvi mune zvekodzero dzakati nemusi weMuvhuro kuti zvakaitika izvi chimwe chiratidzo chinoshungurudza chekuwedzerwa kwekutya mimvuri nechati kwatara nekumbunyikidzwa kuri kuitwa nehurumende.
Catherine Eden, gweta remubatanidzwa wemasangano anorwira kodzero dzevanhu muTanzania, reTanzania Human Rights Defenders Coalition, anoti zvakaitika izvi zvakabva pakusanzwisisana.
Akati vakokwa vakange vabva kuSouth Africa kumusangano wenyika gumi neshanu uyu vakange vachida kuita muchinguva chipfupi chiitiko chekurangarira zvakaitika pakapfurwa vashandi vemumigodhi kuMarikana kuSouth Africa makore manomwe apfuura musi wa 16 Nyamavhuvhu.
Vashandi makumi matatu nevana vemumigodhi vakaurayiwa nemapurisa pachiitiko chisanganisira mapurisa chakaipisisa chisati chamboitika kubva pakapera kutonga kwehudzvanyiriri hwechichena mugore ra1994.
Saka vakokwa vakange vari pachiitiko chaiitika necheparutivi vakaimba rwiyo rwenyika rwemuSouth Africa, ndokutora chinguva chekunyarara vachiyeuka nekuremekedza vashakabvu uye ndokuzokumbira hurumende yavo kuti idzivirire vanhu vayo nezhira dziri nani.
Asi chimwe chinhu chavakanyora pachipepa chakaita kuti mapurisa agutsikane kuti vakokwa ava vaive nehurongwa hwekuita zvimwe zvinhu zvikurusa.
Vakanyora mamwe mashoko pamapepa makuru, uye zvainge zvanyorwa pamazipepa aya zvaiti, "Regai kuuraya vanhu vedu" akadaro. "...
Saka ndinofunga kuti mumusangano uyu maive nemunhu anoona nezvekuchengetedzwa kwenyika, uye paakaona mashoko aya akabva afunga kuti hwaive hurongwa hwekuratidzira.
Asi ukanyatsotarisisa, haugone kuona kuti sei vaizoda kuratidzira pamusoro pekupfurwa kwevanhu kuMarikana kuSouth Africa, asi ivo vari muTanzania."
Hazvina kujeka kana panotori nemunhu akasungwa.
Mamwe masangano ezvekodzero anoti zvizvarwa zvekune dzimwe nyika zvakasunga, asi hazvina kubvunzurudzwa.
Kutya, kunzwa kusachengetedzeka'
Eden anoti akasheedzwa kuzoona vakuru apo ayienda kukamba yemapurisa manheru eChishanu kunoona mumwe wevaronga ari chizvarwa chemuTanzania asi ndokuzonzi aende hake asi apihwa yambiro yekusazviita futi.
Mushure mazvo, mapurisa akazoenda mumipanda yemumahotera maigara vakokwa ava vachitsvaga zvinhu zvaifungidzira kuti zvinogona kukanganisa kuchengetedzeka kwenyika. Hapana chavakawana, akataura achidaro.
Janet Zhou, mukuru wesangano rinoona nezvehukama huri pakati pezvikwereti zveZimbabwe negoneso yekuunza kubudirira munyika yeZimbabwe Coalition on Debt and Development, aive mumwe wevarwiri vekodzero vakabvunzurudzwa nemapurisa pahotera paaigara.
Ndakange ndavakutya, ndainzwa kuti handina kuchengetedzeka, ndisingawanze mashoko ndakasiiwa ndizere kutya nekushungurudzwa mukati mangu, akaudza VOA, mushure mekudzoka kumusha ku Harare. "Nekuti kuona vanhu vezvekuchengetedzwa kwenyika vachiuya nguva dzadarika pakati pehusiku, vachindibvunzurudza pamusoro pekuratidzira nezvinyorwa zviri pamapepa makuru andakange ndisingagone kuvapa, chaive chimwe chinhu chisionekwe. Handina kuzvihwisisa. Zvakandisiya ndichigwagwadza nekutya.
"Nekuti kuona vanhu vezvekuchengetedzwa kwenyika vachiuya nguva dzadarika pakati pehusiku, vachindibvunzurudza pamusoro pekuratidzira nezvinyorwa zviri pamapepa makuru andakange ndisingagone kuvapa, chaive chimwe chinhu chisionekwe. Handina kuzvihwisisa. Zvakandisiya ndichigwagwadza nekutya.
Akati mapurisa akazomuudza iye nevamwe vakokwa aaive navo makumi mana kuti vagare pahotera vasabude zuva rese remusi weMugovera.
Akavabvunza kuti vakange vavasunga here, asi havana kumupindura.
Zvinonyatsa Kunzwisisika'
Oryem Nyeko, munzveri anogara kuKampala achishandira sangano rinotarisisa nyaya dzekodzero dzevanhu reHuman Rights Watch, akati mapurisa emuTanzania haana chaakaita chinganzi chaive kuzhe kwemutemo.
Asi akati, izvozvo hazviitewo zvavakaita kuti zvive zvinhu zvakanaka.
Ndinofunga kuti chaive chunhu chinohwisisika kuti mapurisa achiite, akadaro.
"Asi zvakadaro, izvi zvinotaurawo pamusoro pedambudziko guru riri muTanzania pakuvhara dariro rekuti vanorwira kodzero dzevanhu vaitewo basa ravo uye mukana wevanhu ava kuti varatidze nekutaura zvavanoda.
Ichi chinongova chidimbu chidoko doko chetsika yekudzvanyirirwa kwezvikwta zvinoshanda nezvekodzero nezvimwe zvinobata veruzhinji munyika ino."
Masangano anoshanda ari munyika dzakawanda akaita se sangano rinorwoira vatapi vanhau reCommittee to Protect Journalists akayambirawo nezvekuwedzerwa kwekudzvinyirirwa.
Musangano mukuru wemuSADC usati waitwa, sangano rinoongorora iri rakatura kushushikana kwaro pamusoro pe "kufukurwa nekun'en'enwa kwerusununguko rwemasangano anotapa nhau," uye "nekukurwiswa kwevatapi venhau semadungamunhu, kumiswa kwekushanda kwemasangano enhau, kuvharwa kwemadandemutande nekuiswa kwemitemo inombunyikidza nekudzivisa."
CPJ yakataura zvikuru sei nezvevatapi venhau vekuTanzania, Azory Gwanda, uyo asiri kuzivikanwa kwaari kubva mugore ra2017, na Erick Kabendera, uyo akasungwa mwedzi wakapfuura achipomerwa mhosva dzezvehupfumi, izvo zvinonzi nesangano iri kutsiva manyorero ake enhau anoongorora nekupenengura.
Kabendera anoramba ari mujeri.
NeMuvhuro, Eden, gweta rake, akati dare redzimhosva rakange rasarudza kumbomisa kutongwa kwenyaya yake, kuti ripe vachuchusi nguva yekutsvaga humboo.
Izi zvichaita kuti agare muchitirongo kwerimwezve zvondo, kusvikira musi wa30 Nyamavhuvhu.
Katsika Kanoshungurudza'
Anna Henga, mukuru wesangano rezvemutemo nekodzero dzevanhu reLegal and Human Rights Center, akati zviito zvemapurisa zvinongowedzera katsika kanoshungurudza kava muTanzania iri kutungamirirwa navaJohn Magafuli, avo vanonzi nevanoongorora nekunzvera vava kunyanya kutonga zvine chisimba nekudzvanyirira.
Izvi zvinoreva kuendera mberi kwedariro rakamanikana remabasa anezvechekuita nezvekodzero nezvido zvevagari vemunyika.
Nekuti izvi zvange zvichiitika kubva muna 2016.
Pane nyaya dzakawanda, pane kufambira mberi kusina kunaka kwakananga kudopokesa dariro revanhu vanorwira kodzero dzevanhu.
Uye zvakananga kukanganisa nanhu vakaita sevaye vari mumasangano anorwira kodzero dzevanhu, masangano enhau, zvichidzivisa nekukanganisa rusununguko rwevanhu kutaura zavanoda nezvavanofunga nerusununguko rwekusangana nekuungana sezvavanoda.
Vanhu Vashoma Vanoungana Kuti Varatidzire KuBulawayo
Vanhu vashoma vakauya kuzopinda pakuratiszira kwakange kwarongwa nebato rinokwikwidza munezvematongerwo kuBulawayo, guta guru rechipiri muZimbabwe, nemusi weMuvhuro sezvo mapurisa akange akazara kwese kwese mumigwagwa nepavazhe dzedare redzimhosva apo bato rinokwikwidza riri kuda kuti riite kuratidzira kwaro imomo.
Mabasa ekutenga nekutengeseana munzvimbo dzeguta dzinowanzowandira veruzhinji kufamba kuzhinji kariitika kuri kwemotokari dzemapurisa, matangi emapurisa ane mvura inovava nemirwi yemapurisa vaimemaira mumigwagwa netsoka.
Bato rinopikisa reMovement for Democratic Change, rakange radeedzera kuratidzira uku chiri chikamu chehurongwa hwekuungana richiratidzira kuti rimanikidze mutungamiriri vaEmmerson Mnangagwa kuti vabvume kuita hurumende yemubatanidzwa yekudzikamisa nekuyambutsa nyika nekuda kwezvehupfumi zviri kuramba zvichiwedzera kuwondomoka nekusimuka kwekukakavadzana nekusawirirana pane zvematongerwo.
Asi mapurisa akadzivisa kuratidzira uku muguta riri kuchamhembe kwenyika, vachiti vaiitira kuti pave nekuchengetedzeka nerunyararo muguta.
Mumwe mutongi wedare redzimhosva muBulawayo ari kunzwa zvirikutaurwawo nebato rinopikisa richikwidzana nekudziviswa uku.
Kuratidzira uku kwakange kwarongwa kuti kutevere kuratidzira kwakange kwaitwa muguta guru, Harare, nemusi weChishanu, uku zviuru zvakati kuti zvevairatidzira zvakafora zvisina basa nekudziviswa kwemapurisa uko kwakange kwatsigirwa nedare redzimhosva repamusoro.
Mapurisa akashandisa hutsi hunokachidza nekutosvoro nekurova vanhu netsvimbo kuti vamiise kuratidzira kwemuHarare.
Vanhu VemuZimbabwe Vanoti Mapurisa Akashandisa Chisimba Nehutsinye Pakaitwa Kuratidzirwa Pane Zvehupfumi Hwenyika
Vanhu vemuZimbabwe vakamhura kudzviswa kwemapurisa neChishanu vaita kuratidzira pamusoro pekunyanya kuwodomoka kwezvehupfumi munyika.
Kunyangwe paine kudziviswa kwakabva kudare guru redzimhosva pakuratidzira, nhengo dzeMovement for Democratic Change dzakapinda mumigwagwa dzikadhumhana nemapurisa.
Vamwe vevakakuvadzwa vakapomera mapurisa ,hosva yekukanganisa gwara nechinangwa chekuratidzira uku, kwaifanirwa kukurudzira hurumende yemutungamiriri vaEmmerson Mnangagwa kuti ifemere mweya wehupenyu mune zvehupfumi hwenyika hwabatwa nechando.
Misodzi ichiyerera pamatama ake, Tafadzwa Bvuta, ane makore makumi matatu nemaviri akati zvidzidzo zvake zvezvikoro zvapamusoro hazvina kumubatsira kuti awane cheuviri kuti achengete vana vake vatatu.
Vakati rova, akadaro achireva mapurisa.
"Chii chataita? Mauto nemapurisa ose aya vanofanirwa kutichengetedza tese, kwete munhu mumwe chete. Tichaendepi kuti tirarame? Saka tinofanirwa kuuraya vana vedu here sezvo tiri kutatarika kuti tivachengete?"
Make Nyashanu, uyo ane makore makumi maviri nemanomwe, akati aizoramba achiratidzira nekuti atambura nekuva rovha.
Akati mapurisa kange achirova munhu wese airatidzira asingasarure, kusanganisira vechikuru, nevaya vakanga vasiri kuratidzira.
"Ndiro kutsaruzhinji racho here iri?" akabvunza, ndokuzowedzera achiti kwaiva kuratidzira kwaive nerunyararo asi mapurisa ndiwo akange ozokonzera mvongamupopoto.
Bato rinopikisasa rakati raizoita kumwe kuratidzira neMuvhuro muguta guru rechipiri muZimbabwe, Bulawayo, uye vachaenda kune mamwe maguta nedzimwe nzvimbo kusvikira hurumende yagadzirisa zvehupfumi.
Mhinduro Yehurumende
Gurukota rezvekufambiswa kwemashoko, Mai Monica Mutsvangwa vakati kuratidzira uku kwaikwikwidzana nebudiriro inounza pundutso, vachizve kuratidzira kwemunaNdira uku pamusoro pekukwira kwemitengo yemafuta kwakaita kuti mabhizimisi arasikirwe nemari iri pakati pemamiriyoni makumi maviri nematatu emadhora nekuda kwekubiwa kwezvvinhu nemazuva pakange pasina zvaitengwa nekutengeswa nekuda kwekuratidzira.
Hurumende inokurudzira vanhu vese vemuZimbabwe vanoda budiriro kuti varambe kushandiswa nevanhu vanosundwa nezvakaipa kuti vakonzere kusagadzikana munyika yavo, nekuti izvi zvinongowedzera kuoma kwezhinhu, uko hurumende iri kushanda pasina zororo kuti igadzirise nezhira inoenderera mberi, vakadaro.
"Ndinoda kudzokorora nekusimbisa zvakataurwa nemukuru wenyika Vanoremekedzwa vaED Mnangagwa kuti vanhu vese vemuZimbabwe vanoda nyika yavo vanofanirwa kushandisa nhaurirano sezhira yekugadzirisa zvidenho nezvinetswa zvatakatarisana nazvo senyika.
Daniel Molokhele, mutauriri webato rinopikisa, akati bato rake raainge risingade kuti vaMnangagwa vatungamirire nhaurirano idzi uye ndokuvanenedzera kuti vakange vabiridzira musarudzo dzakapedzesera kuitwa muZimbabwe muna2018.
Akati kuratidzira uku kwaizoenderera mberi kusvikira zvehupfumi hwenyika hadzokera panzvimbo pahwo chaipo.
UN Inoshora Kutsikirira Pasi Kwekuratidzira Kuri Kuitwa Murunyararo Nehurumende yeZimbabwe
Hofisi yeU.N. inoona nezvekodzero dzevanhu iri kushora kutsikirira pasi nemusi weChishanu nemapurisa anodzivisa mhirizhonga pavanhu vairatidzira murunraro muguta guru reHarare.
Bazi iri riri kuti ngapave nekuongorora nekutsvakiridza mukushandiswa kwechisimba chiri kuzhe kwemwero nemapazi anochengetedza runyararo munyika.
Mutauririri weU.N. Human Rights, Rupert Colville anoti pane zhira dziri nani dzekugadzirisa kuchema kwekurevesa kuri kubva muvanhu vemunyika pamusoro pemamiriro ezvehupfumi munyika pane kutsikirira nekurova vanhu vari kuratidzira murunyararo.
Tiri kushushikana zvikuru nemadambudziko ezvemagariro nezvehupfumi ari kuramba achirudunuka muZimbabwe.
Kunyange hazvo ndichigamuchira zviri kuedzwa kuitwa nehurumende, mhuri yenyika dzepasi rose ne U.N. muZimbabwe kuti pave nekuderedza zvinorwadza zvirikubva padambudziko iri uye nezvirikuitwa kuunza shanduko, nyatwa yezvehupfumi yavakurovawo kodzero panezvehupfumi nemagariro emamiriyoni evanhu vemuZimbabwe, Colville akadaro.
Vagari vemuZimbabwe vari kutambura nekukwira kwemitengo kuri kunzerwa nemari yenyika iri kushaiwa simba rekutenga, zvo zvaita kuti mitengo iite zvekusvetukira mudenga pazvinhu zvinodiwa neruzhinji zuva nezuva zvakadai semafuta ezvifambiso, chikafu, mari yekufambisa nehutano.
Zvabva zvawedzera kujambwa iri kuparadzwa kuri kubva kudutumupengo Idai iro rakarova Zimbabwe munaKurume, uyewo nekushaiwa mvura zvakakonzera kuti zvirimwa zvitsire muminda.
United Nations inoti chikamu chimwe chete kubva muzvitatu chevagari vemuZimbabwe vanosvika mamiriyoni gumi nematanhatu vanoda kubatsirwa kuti vararame zvezuva nezuva
Hudzamu hwezvakakonzerwa nekukuvadzwa nekusungwa kunogona kwakaitika mushure mekuratidzira kweChishanu hahusati hwanyatsojeka. Asi Colville anoudza VOA kuti hofisi yake yakagamuchira chinyorwa cheongororo chaitaura nezvekutyorwa kwekodzero dzevanhu mumwedzi mishoma ichangodarika.
