Hurumende yeZimbabwe yaraira vashandi vayo vakabaiya jekiseni rekudzivirira denda reCOVID-19 kuti vachidzokera kubasa ikezvino mushure menguva inodarika gore vachishanda vari kumba, ichiti huwandu hwevanhu vari kubatwa nedenda iri huri kuderera munyika.
Vakuru vakazivisawo kuti vashandi vese vehurumedne vasina humboo hwekubaiwa dziviriro vacharambidzwa kupinda munzvimbo dzavanoshandira, uye vanozorangwa, kusanganisira kumbomisirwa marodzavo dzemihoro.
