Munguva ichangodarika, nyika dzekumaodzanyemba dzakashora kusvika muguta guru reMali, Bamako, kwevarwi vemakambani echiuto akazvimiririra anonzi ndeekuRussia, izvo zviri kurambwa nemasoja akabvuta masimba munyika iyi muna2020.
Panguva apo hukama neFrance huchiramba huchishata, vatongi vechiuto ava vanogona kunge vachitsvaga dzimwe nzira dzekuvhara gwanza riripo nekuda kwekuderera kuru kuramba kuchiitika kwemauto anobva kuEurope anga achirwisana nekumukira kwemakore kwechi jihad muMali
Varwi vemakambani echiuto akazvimiririra anonzi maMercs [kana kuti mercenaries] vanoshandira muAfrica yatova garoziva, zvichibva muchikamu pamakore nemakore emabasa aiitwa nemakambani echiuto akazvimiririra ekuSouth Africa, akadaro Jason Blazakis wesangano rekuNew York renyanzvi dzekuongorora nekunzvera rinonzi Soufan.
Shasha dzeWagner idzi dziri kupinda nepamagonhi anga agara akazarurirwa kuvanhu verudzi nemabasa avo, akapamhidzira achidaro.
Hapana vakaturwa zviri pachena pamusoro pekukura kwesangano iri kana hwuwandu hwemari yaiinayo.
Asi mukati meAfrica, sangano rinoita zvidzidzo neongororo yezvenzira dzekuita zvinhu dzakatesvera uye kuongorora zvomoitika munyika dzakasiyana siyana reCenter for Strategic and International Studies (CSIS) riri muWashington rakawana humboo kubva muna 2016 hwemauto anobva kuRussia anoita basa nekuti abhadharwa zvisineyi nechikonzero chacho achiwanikwa muSudan, South Sudan, Libya, the Central African Republic (CAR), Madagascar neMozambique.
Botswana, Burundi, Chad, the Comoros, the Democratic Republic of Congo, Congo-Brazzaville, Guinea, Guinea-Bissau, Nigeria and Zimbabwe are also on the CSIS's list.
MuAfrica "maita kusangana nekuvhengana kwezvido zvenyika dzakawanda, kusanganisira zvido zve China," Alexey Mukhin anoshana nesangano rinongorora zvemashoko ezvematongerwo riri muMoscow rinonzi Centre for Political Information akaudza AFP.
Nyika yega yega ine kodzero yekudzivirira hupfumi nezvinokosha zviri mairi, akaenderera mberi achidaro.
Kuvhumuka'
Wagner hairarami kana kushanda zviri pamutemo, haina kunyoreswa sekambani, haibhadhari mitero kana kuva nezvinyorwa zvinoratidza kuti ndiani anoita chii zvinogona kuwanikwa kana kuzivikanwa.
EU payakada kurova boka iri nezvirango zvemari muna 2020, yakabva yananga mbozha yekuRussia inotsigira hutongi hweko anonzi Yevgeny Prigozhin, uyo anowirirana nemutungamiriri weRussia, Vladimir Putin uye achifungidzirwa kuti ndiye muridzi weWagner.
Yakazowedzera zvimwe zvirango munaZvita gore rakapfuura apo kusvika kwevarwi vemakambani echiuto aya muMali kwakanga kwava pachena, asi Russia ikabva yati vanhu vaitaura izvi vakange vachi "vhumuka".
Nyanzvi mune zvechiuto munyika dzekumaodzanyemba dzinoti makambani echiuto aya anenge akasimwa muzvikwata zvekuzvidzivirira zvenyika zvakaita sezvevasvori nemauto, izvo zvinoita kuti kuramba kweRussia kuti kune makambani echiuto akazvimiririra kuve nyore kukugamuchira.
Kutumirwa kwawo kunyika dzemuAfrica kune chinangwa 'chekubatsira Russia kuti... Idzokere nekuwana zvakare chinzvimbo chekuva nesimba pamusoro pezvinoitwa kana kuronga" chinova chinzvimbo chadonha nekurasika panguva yekuarara kwemubatanidzwa wenyika zhinji dzainzi Soviet Union, akadaro munzveri weCSIS, Catrina Doxsee.
Huvepo hwevashandi emakambani emauto eya hwange huchiwedzera nekukasirisa, kubva pakaitwa musangano mukuru weRussia nenyika dzemuAfrica muna 2019.
Russia yange ichiita basa "zvikuru sei munzvimbo dzaisivikanwa sekuti dzinorunzirwa neFrance" munyika dzaive pasi pehutongi hweFrance dzakaita seCAR neMali, akadaro Djallil Lounnas, munzveri anoshanda ari pachikoro chepamusoro soro muMorocco cheAl Akhawayn university.
Kunyangwe hazvo makambani echiuto akazvimiririra aya dzimwe nguva achifambisa kutengeswa kwezvombo zvinogadzirwa neRussia "mari inopinda apa haina chainoreva kana ichizoenzaniswa nemari svinu yavanogona kuburitsa kubva pamvumo pakuchera migodhi kana kodzero yekushandisa zviwanikwa zvinokosha munyika," Doxsee akadaro.
Izvi zvinoita kuti nyika dzisina kugadzika asi dziine zvicherwa kana hupfumi hwemafuta dzive nyika dzine hufpimi dzingada kuitirwa basa nemauto aya, sekuSyria uko vakrwi ava vakange vozivikanwa nevanhuwo zvavo eruzhinji rwemunyika.
Hapana mibvunzo inobunzwa
Lounnas akati chimwe chakanakira vanoitirwa basa ndechekusazonetsana panyaya dzekodzero dzevanhu negutsaruzhinji zvinogona kuuya nemakambani anobva kunyika dzekumavirira.
Russia ine zvainodawo. Haibvunze mibvunzo, akapamhidzira achidaro.
Kutaurwa kwehutsinye nechisimba chinokuvadza nekubatwa zvisina kunaka kwevanhu kunopa pfungwa yekuti kuda izvi ndizvowo zvinoitwa kuvarwi vemakambani akazvimiririra pachezvavo.
MuCAR, United Nations iri kuferefeta kuurayiwa kwevanhu vazhinji panguva imwe chete pabasa remubatanidzwa wemauto vehurumende nevarwi veWagner.
Mumwe munhu ari muchiuto akaudza AFP kuti vanhu vanodarika makumi mashanu vakafa, vamwe "vachifa vachiitwa zvekupfurwa nepfuti."
Nemusi weChina, sangano reEuropean Union yakati yakange isiri kuzosimudzira kudzidziswa kwezvechiuto CAR ”izvo zvakange zvambomiswa pakati paZvita "kusvikira mauto emunyika umu arega kushandira Wagner."
Zvichakadai zvinoitwa nezvikwata zvemauto ekunze aya hazviwanzoenderana nezvinenge zvichitarisirwa nehurumende dzinenge dzavapa mabasa ekuita.
MuLibya, varwi vemakambani echiuto akazvimiririra ekuRussia akarasakirwa nehupenyu nezvishandiswa mukuedza kwegore rose kwaMarshal Khalifa Haftar kuti akunde nekutora guta guru reTripoli, chakazova chinhu chisina kuzobudirira pakupedzesera.
Uye muMozambique, varwi vekuRussia ava vakadududza vatarisana nevarwi vechi ihad veboka reIslamic State group jihadists, vachibva vatorerwa basa nevanovakwikwidza nekuSouth Africa.
Kunyangwe vasingagone mutauro wemunyika kana kunzwisisa mamiririro akaita nzvimbo yavanoshandira, mauto eWagner "akasarudzwa nekuti ndivo vakange vaine mari yakanyanya kuderera kudarika vamwe vose", akadaro Doxsee.
Vakange vasina zvinoita kuti vabudirire, akawedzera achidaro, achitiwo "vakasangana nekukonewa kwati wandeyi" muAfrica yose.
Kubva vakunda nekubudirira zvachose kunogona kukanganisa mafambisirwe anoitwa bhizimisi remauto emakambani akazvimiririra nekuti bhidhauko ravo riri pane mhirizhonga, kurwisana nemvongamupopoto.
Kana nyika yakaita seCAR ikavakumbira kuti idzidzise mauto ayo, kuibatsira mumabasa nehurongwa hwayo hwechiuto, zvinenge zvichizovanakira kuti vaite nekupedzesa mabasa aya zvakanaka kuti vagone kuenderera mberi vari pabasa, akadaro Doxsee.
Deno kuri kuti vanobva vaita basa racho nemazvo zvekubva vapedza hondo, zvaizoreva kuti havaizonge vachitsvagwa zve kuti vaite basa.
Dutu Rinonzi Batsirai Rinopera Simba Mushure Mekurova, Mashamu Otyirwa
Dutu rinonzi Batsirai rakapera simba munguva yemanheru asi kunyangwe zvakadaro mashamu achiri kutarisirwa nekuda mvura yakasimba yakanyay kumabvazuva eMadagascar aine mhepo isine simba guru, bazi rezvemamiriro ekunze muchitsuwa ichi akadaro nemusi weSvondo.
Batsirai yaderea simba rayo, Meteo Madagascar yakadaro, asi ndokuzotiwo kumhanya kwedutu iri kwakange kwadupuka zvekugurwa nepakati ravakufamba mutunhu wemamaira makumimasere muawa rimwe chete, uyewo mhepo yakange yadzikira kusvika pakufamba mutunhu wezana negumi remamaira muawa rimwechete kubva pamamaira mazana mairi nemakumi matatu nemashanu paawa akaonekwa dutu parakamhara muchitsuwa ichi nemusi weMugovera manheru.
Dutu iri, rinova rechipiri kurova chitsuwa chikuru ichi chiri mugungwa reIndian Ocean mumasvondo mashomanana, rakakange rakananga kumavirazuva richifamba zvekusvika mutunhu wemamaira gumi nemasere paawa rimwe chete, bazi rezvemamiriro ekunze rakadaro.
Asi "madutu anenge ari epanzvimbo imwe chete kana anenge akapararira munzvimbo dzakasiyana siya" anowanzotyirwa kuti anoitika mushure kwekunaya kwemvura zhinji" yakadaro ichitiwo Batirai yaigona kuzotangawo munyanza muchikamu chakatarisana nenyika yemozambique chinonzi Mozambique Channel zuva roda kurereka nemusi weSvondo.
Batsirai yakamhara mudunhu reMananjary, mutunhu unodarika makiromita mazana mashanu nemakumi matatu nechekuchamhembe kwakadzivira kumabvazuva eguta guru reAntananarivo, munguva dzesere mauro (kana kuti kuti nenguva dzeshanu zuva rodoka pachishandiswa chieranguva cheGeneral Meridian) neMugovera.
Rakange rasvika muchitsuwa "sedutu rakasimba" riine mhepo dzaimhanya zvekusvika muawa rimwe chete kumatunhu ari kure zvemamaira zana nemakumi matanhatu ane mashanu, Faly Aritiana Fabien uyu anoshanda pasi bebazi rinoona nezvekunatsira munguva dzetsaona nenjodzi munyika akaudza AFP.
Bazi rinoona nezvemamiriro ekunze munyika rakange rati rinotyira "kuparadzwa kukuru uye kwakapararira munzvimbo dzakawanda."
Kwangopera awa rimwe chete nechidimbu, rakabva ramhara ndokutanga kurakasha, vanhu vangasvike zviuru makumi mavu nemanomwe vakange vaverengwa seavo vakange vabviswa kubva pamisha yavo, akadaro, Fabien.
Vakati hofisi yavo yakange yagadzirira nekurongedza nzvimbo dzekugara, zvekudya nemishonga kuitira vanenge vakanganuswa nedutu iri, uewo patove nehurongwa hwekutsvaga nekudzikunura hwakatomirira kushandiswa.
Njodzi Huru'
Sangano rinoongorora mamiriro ekunze rekuFrance reMeteo-France rakange rafanotaura kuti raitarisira kuti Batsirai raizounza "njodzi huru" kuMadagascar, mushure mekupfuura nemuMauritius uye nekupura nemubvumbi chitsuwa chiri pasi peFrance chinonzi La Reunion kwemazuva maviri.
Mumaawa mashona dutu risati rarova, vagari vakahwarara pasi munyika yakaromboka iyi vachiri kumbopora kubva mumavanga edutumupengo rine njodzi rinonzi Tropical Storm Ana mukupera wemwedzi wakapfuura.
Muguta reVatomandry iro riri kumabvazuva kumhenderekedzo egungwa, vanhu vanodarika mazana maviri vakange vakapakirana mubandiko rimwe chete mune chimwe chivakwa chekongiri chechizvarwa chekuChina.
Mhuri dzakarara parupasa nepamametiresi asina mibhedha.
Mutungamiriri we munzvimbo Thierry Louison Leaby akakungura kushaikwa kwemvura yakachena mushure mekunge kambabi inooona nezvemvura muguta yadzima mvura ichigadzirira kuuya kwedutu iri.
Vanhu vari kubika nemvura inesvina, akadaro, paine kutyira kupararira kwechirwere chemanyoka.
Pazhe, madhishi namabhagidhi epurastiki akange akiswa mumitsara akateedza achichingidzira mvura yaidonhakuvha kumarata ekapfirira matenga edzimba.
Hurumende inosungirwa kuti batsira zvachose. Hatina chatati tapihwa, akadaro.
Vagari vakasarudza kuramba vari mudzima dzavo vakashandisa masaga akazara jecha nemaba mahombe ekutakurisa mafuta emotokari kuti zvisimbise matenga edzimba dzavo asatakurwe nedutu.
Dutu richiine 'njodzi'
Vamwewo vagari vemuVatomandry vakange vachiunganidza zvinhu zvekushandisa vachigadzirira kuuya kwedutu iri.
Tanga tichiunganidza kwesvondo, mupunga nemabarwe negorosi, asi nekudzimwa dzimwa kemagetsi, hatisi kukwanisa kuchengeta nyama nehove, akadaro Odette Nirina uyo ava nemakore makumi matanhatu nemashanu ari muridzi wehotera iri muVatomandry.
Ndakaunganidzawo marasha.
Kuno takajairira madutu, akaudza AFP.
Mhepo dzinovhuvhuta dzichimhanya kwemamairi anodarika makumi mashanu paawa rimwe chete dzakarova Vatomandry nemusi weSvondo mangwanani, dzichiteverwa nemvura yaipota ichinaya yombokasa.
Bandiko rinoshanda kubatsira panguva dzenjodzi iri rakati dutu iri raitarisirwa kuramba riine "njodzi" paraizopfuura nemuchitsuwa chikiri ichi mauro ese uye nemumangwanani.
Madutu ari kutarisirwa nekuda kwekunaya kwemvura yakawandisa kumabvazuva, kuchamhembe kwakadziva kumabvazuva enyika nekumatunhu ari pakati penyika, yakayambira ichidaro.
United Nations yakange iri mushishi kukwenenzvera gadziriro yayo mukushanda nemasangano anobatsiora panguva dzetsaona, kugarisa ndege dzinobatsira vanenge panguva dzakadai dzakagadzirira kuita basa, uyewo nekuunganida chikafu nezvimwe zvinodiwa pakubatsira vanhu vari munjodzi.
Vanhu vasiri pasi pezviru zana nemakumi matatu nerimwe vakakanganiswa ne dutu Ana munyika yese yeMadagascar mukupera kwaNdira.
Vanhu potse kwemakumi matanhatu vakauraiyiwa, ruzhinji rwavo muguta guru reAntananarivo.
Dutu iri rakarovawo Malawi, Mozambique neZimbabwe, rikakonzera ndufu dzevanhu vakati wandeyi.
Bazi rinoona nezvekudya kwakanaka nechikafu muU.N. reWorld Food Program rakataura pamusoro zvaitarisirwa nevakuru vemunyika dzakasiyana zvekuti vanhu vanosvika zviuru mazana mashanu nemakumi mapfumbamwe nezvishanu vaizokanganiswa nedutu Batsirai iri, uye czviuru zana nemakumi mashanu evanhuwo vaizobviswa munzvimbo dzananogara nekuda kwekuyerera kwevhu zhinji richifukidza misha uyewo nemafashanu emvura kwese kwese.
Dutu iri rinounza njodzi dzakasiyana siyana kuvanhu vasiri pasi pemamiriyoni mana nezviuru mazana mana, sangano rinobatsira munguva dzenjodzi nehondo pasi rose reInternational Federation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies rakadaro.
Finland Inopihwa Korona Yekuva Nyika Ine Mufaro Kudarika Dzimwe Kwegore Rechishanu
Finland yakanzi ndiyo nyika ine mufaro kudarika dzimwe nyika kwemakore mashuni akateedzana gore rino, muongororo yakaitwa netsigiro yeU.N., iyo yakatiwo Afghanstan ndiyo yakange yakasuruvara kudarika dzimwe zdose ichiteverwa nepedyo pedyo neLebanon.
Serbia, Bulgaria neRomania dzakaratidza kuwedzera kuwakawanda kwerudekaro.
Kudonha kukura muMatanera Emufaro Munyika Dzepasi Rose, ayo akaburitswa neChishanu, kwakange kuri paLebanon, Venezuela neAfghanistan.
Lebanon, iyo iri kutarisana nekukweshana nekuparara kwezvehupfumi, yakadonera kuva yechipiri kubva kumuswe mumanera ane nyika zana nemakumi mana nenhanhatu iri pasi zvishomanani peZimbabwe.
Afghanistan, iyo iri kushungurudzwa nehondo, ndiyo iri panyasi pemanera aya, yakasangana nekuwedzera kwedambudziko revanhu vanoda kubatsirwa nekuda kwenhamo kubva maTaliban akabvuta zvakare masimba ekutonga nyika gore rakapera muna Nyamavhvhu wegore rakapera. Bandiko reU.N. rinoona nezvevana nekudzidza kwavo reUNICEF rinofungidzira kuti vana miriyoni vari pasi pemakore mashanu vanogona kufa nenzara mumwaka wematsutso wegore rino kana vakasabatsirwa.
Manera aya anopa chiyeuchidzo chiri pachena chekuparadza kwezvinhu zvinooneka zvezvisingaoneke kana kubatika kunounzwa nehondo kuvanhu vazhinji vainokanganisa nekurwadzisa, akadaro Jan-Emmanuel De Neve munyori webhuku remanera iri raakanyora nevamwe vanyori. Ongororo Yemufaro Pasi Rose, iyo yave mugore regumi ichiburitswa, inonyorwa maringe nemaonero anoita vagari vemunyika pamusoro pemufaro wavo, uyewo uchishandisa ongororo yezvehupfumi nemagariro evnahu.
Inopa zvibodzwa zvemufaro zvinobva pasina chibodzwa kusvikira pagumi, ichishandisa ongororo inenge yakaitwa kwemakore matatu akapfuura. Chuinyorwa chichongodhindiswa chakaburwa Russia isati yapinda muUkraine zvine chisimba chehondo
Nyika dziri kumaodzanyemba eEurope ndidzo zvakare dzakatora zvinzimbo dzepamusoro, Denmark iri panzimbo pechipiri ichitevera Finland, kwozoteverawo Iceland, Switzerland kuchizouyawo maDutch. United States yakakwira nezvidanho zvitatu kuenda pachinzvimbo chegumi nezviotanhatu, chibodzwa chimwe pamusoro peBritain, ukuwo France ichibva yakwira kusvika pachimbo chemakumi maviri, chidanho chayo chepamusoro soro chayanga isati yambochisvikira.
Kuzhe kwehudekaro hwedungamunhu, uhwo hwaishandisa ongororo yaibva mukubvunza vanhu vanomiririra zvipoka nezvikwata zvakasiyana hweugari hwevanhu munyika yega yega hweGallup, zvibodzwa zvemufaro izvi zviotarisawo hupfumi hunogadzirwa nevanhu vemunyika iyi, rustigiro kumagariro akanaka evanhu zvikuri sei vanoshaiwa uyewo huwandu nehudzamu hwekuhuori hwuri mairi.
Gore rino vanyori vakashandisawo zvakabuda mutvsakurudzo yezvinyorwa zvemadariro ekutandararira pamadandemutande kuti iyenzanise zvinzwo zvevanhu denda reCovid risati ravepo uye mushure mekunge rauya. Vakaona "kuwedzera kwakadzama kwekutya nekusuruvara" munyika gumi nesere, asi kudererawo pakunzwa hasha.
Dzidziso yeOngororo Yemufaro Pasi Rose mumakore apfuura ndeyekuti rutsigiro mumagariro evanhu, kuva nemwoyo nermaoko ekupanana nechipavhurire mumwe kune mumwe uye kurevesa muhurumende zvakakosha kuitira rudekaro, akanyora achidaro mumwe wevanyori vegwaro iri, anonzi Jeffrey Sachs.
Vatungamiriri Vepasi Vanofanirwa Kuchenjera.
Chinyorwa ichi chakonzera kusagutsikana pachakaisa Finland pachinzvimbo chekutanga muna2018.
Vanhu vazhinji munyika ine vanhu mamiriyoni mashanu nezviuru mazana mashanu vanozviti vanhu vasingatane kubatwa nekusuruvara, uye kana vaona vanhu vari kuratidza mufaro wavo pane veruzvinji vanofungidzira kuti hapana kurevesa.
Asi nyika iyi yemasango emiti nemadziva makurusa inozivikanwawo nehurongwa hwezvinoshandiswa neveruhinji zvinoshanda zvakaisvonakisa, dzimba dzekutambarira nekutwasanudza miviri vachidziiswa nehutsi hwemvura inopisa nekusvinwa mitezo nenyanzvi kuitira kuti pfungwa dzizorore uye kuti ropa rifambe mumuviri zvakanaka, uyewo vanovimba zvikuru muvanhu vakaiswa pazcvimbo zvesimba uyewo mune huwandu hushoma hwehugeven'a nekupara mhosva uye kusaenzana kwevanhu mumagariro.
Dare Redzimhosva MuZimbabwe Rinorayira Kutongwa Kwetapi Wenhau Anombonyorera NY Times
Rimwe dare redzimhosva muZimbabwe rakandira kunze chikumbiro chesatongwa chakaitwa neChipiri munyaya yemhosva iri kunenedzerwa mumwe mutapi wenhau weNew York Times. Mutapi wenhau anonyorera masangano enhau akasiyana siyana, journalist Jeffrey Moyo ari kupomerwa mhosva yekutyora mitemo yekupinda nekubuda kwevanhu muZimbabwe apo achinzi akabatsira vatapi venhau vekune dzimwe nyika vaviri kuti vapinde munyika iyi iri kuchamhembe kweAfrica zviri kunze kwemutemo gore rakapera.
Kathleen Mpofu mumwe wemagweta aMoyo akati mutapi wenhau uyu achamira pamberi pedare kuti atongwe musi wa28 Kubvumbi.
Mutongi wedare redzimhosva akaramba kugamuchira chikumbiro chekusatongwa. Akaona kuti vachuchusi vehurumende vakane vaunza humboo hwakakwana zvekuti vaMoyo vanofanirwa kuzvidavirira, uye pakusvika pavakaona izvi, Mpofu akaudza VOA ari kuBulawayo, achishandisa WhatsApp.
Zvinoita sekuti mutongi akashandisa zvekuti vachuchusi vehurumende vakange vatungamidza mberi zvinonzi zvitupa zvekuita basa zvisiri zvechokwadi zvakange zvawanikwa nemutapi wekunze kwenyika, uye achishandisa kunzwisisa kwake kwehumboo hwakaturwa nevachuchusi vehurumende, akaona zvakakwana kuti nyakupomerwa mhosva azvidavirire zvaari kupomerwa.
Magweta aMoyo vaivimba kuti nyaya iyi yazokandwa kunze kwedare, mushure medare rimwe chete rati mumwe mushandi weZimbabwe Media Commission official, Thabang Manhika, akange asina mhosva yekugadzira zvitupa zvenhema zvekupa vatapi venhau vaviri vekuSouth Africa vanoshandira New York Times vakange vapinda muZimbabwe asi mushure kwava kuzodzingwa munyika. Moyo naManhika vakange vachitongwa vakapatsanurwa, mumuwe nemumwe sedungamunhu.
Hurumende yeZimbabwe inoti vese Moyo naManhika vakatyora mitemo yekupinda nekubuda kwevanhu.
Munyori mukuru mubazi rekufambiswa kwemashoko Ndabaningi Nick Mangwana akataura pamusoro pemutongo wakaitwa neChipiri uyu.
Taingoda kuona kuti pane mutemo nekugadzikana kwezvinhu.
Kana mumwe mnhu akapara mhosva kana kuti ari kuonekwa seakapara mhisva, vachawana zuva ravo rekuzvidavirira mudare redzimhosva, saka awana zuva rake mudare redzimhosva, saka zvichaitika kwaari hazvisi mumaoko edu, zviri mumaoka ehurongwa hwemitemo inotonga nekururamisa panenge patyorwa mutemo.
Ndiwo maonero edu, Mangwana akadaro.
Tabani Moyo wesangano rezvenhau rekuchamhembe kweAfrica reMedia Institute of Southern Africa, kana kuti MISA, akati mutapi wenhau uyu anofanirwa kutongwa nenzira yekururamisira pasi divi rinotorwa nevatongi.
MISA Zimbabwe inosimbisa kuti panofanirwa kuva nekutonga kwekuyenzanisira.
Ndiwo maonero edu kusvikira nyaya iyi yapera.
Zvese zvatiri kutaura ndezvekuti iye, semumwewo mugari wemunyika anofanirwa kutongwa nenzira inoenzanisira ,akadaro Moyo.
Moyo, chizvarwa chemuZimbabwe, anogona kugara mujeri kwemakore gumi kana akawanikwa aine mhosva.
Mapurisa EmuZimbabwe Anodzivisa Misangano Yebato Rinopikisa
Mapurisa emuZimbabwe neMugovera akadzivisa bato guru rinopikisa mukuita misangano nevatsigiri vayo pamberi pesarudzo dichaitwa musi wa26 Kurume kuti zvigaro zvisisina vamiririri kubva paitwa sarudzo dzevamiriri muna 2018.
Mapurisa anoti kudziviswa kwemusangano kuMavhunga, mufambo ungasvike makiromita makumi masere kumabvazuva eHarare, kwaitirwa kuti pave nerunyararo nekugadzikana.
Mapurisa akaita musasa wavo husiku hwese pane imwe nzvimbo yekuunganira nemusi weChishanu muMarondera, umo mutungamiriri webato guru rinopikisa muZimbabwe, the Citizens Coalition for Change, Nelson Chamisa, akange achifanirwa kutaura kuvatsigiri vake neMugovera.
Murume wemakore makumi mana nemana arikudawo kukwikwidza pakuva mutungamiriri wenyika akazouya kuzoudza gungano rakange rakamumiririra kuti richidzokera haro kudzimba.
Tiri bato rerunyararo, bato rekutonga kwemutemo, akadaro.
Chamisa akati bato rake haridi kurwa nevanhu.
Akati hurumende yakaramba kupa mvumo yekuita musangano, saka bato rake rakamukumbira kuti auye ataure pamusoro penyaya iyi.
Akaudza vatsigiri vake kuti haadi kuti zvematongerwo zveZimbabwe zvikonzere rufu.
Akawedzerazve kuti chisingazivikanwe nehurumende ndechekuti muno muMarondera, kusvika kwake chete kwakatokwana.
Mukubvunzwa mibvunzo nevatapi venhau nemusi weSvondo, Fadzayi Mahere, mutauririkadzi weCitizens Coalition for Change akati bato rake haris kufadzwa nekurerekera kudivi rimwe chete kwe bazi rinofambisa sarudzo muZimbabwe, reZimbabwe Electoral Commission nemapurisa vachitsigira bato riri kutonga reZANU-PF.
Musangano wedu unonzi wakadziviswa asi ZANU PF yanga iine musangano wanga uchiitwa nemotokari dzakadungamidzana munzvimbo imwe cheteyo, akadaro.
"Hapana musi kana mumwe wavakakumbira mvumo kana kusuma mapurisa, asi kudziviswa uku kuri kunze kwemutemo kunoregedzerwa kwatiri.
Yedu ihondo yekudzivisa tisingashandise mhirizhonga.
Zvisineyi, zviuru zvange zvauya kuzonzwa mutingamiriri Chamisa vachitaura zvaratidza pasina kukahadzika kuti vagari vakagadzirira kuita zvose zvinofanirwa kuitwa kuti vabvute hunhu nekukudzikana kwavo.
Tinoramba tichikurudzira vatsigiri vedu kuti vanonyoresa nehuwandu hwavo kuvagone kusarudza vatungamiriri nevamiririri vavanoda kuti tizadzikise chinangwa chedu muna2023: Kukunda kwakazara pasina kupokana."
Mapurisa emuZimbabwe neSvondo akaramba kutaura pamusoro rekudziviswa kweCitizens Coalition for Change muMarondera. Vakazotura tsamba kumusangano unokwikwidza vachiti vaida nguva yekugadzirira kuti pave nerunyararo pamusangano uyu. Masvondo maviri apfuura, mvongamupopoto nekurovana kwakatangwa nevanhu vanofungidzirwa kuti vatsigir veZANU-PF pamusangano weCitizens Coalition for Change wakasiya kwafa vanhu vaviri nevazhinji vakuvadzwa.
